Come take a look before it is gone. This Subaru includes: ICE SILVER METALLIC INT & EXT AUTO DIM MIRROR W/HL Auto-Dimming Rearview Mirror Universal Garage Door Opener BLACK, PERFORATED LEATHER-TRIMMED UPHOLSTERY Leather Seats *Note - For third party subscriptions or services, please contact the dealer for more information.* The 2020 Subaru Forester Touring is praised for its extensive safety features, spacious and comfortable interior, excellent visibility, and standard all-wheel drive system. Key Advantages Comprehensive Safety Features: The Touring trim includes the full EyeSight suite of active safety features, which was enhanced for 2020 to include lane centering. It also uniquely features the DriverFocus Distraction Mitigation System, which uses facial recognition to monitor for driver fatigue or distraction. The vehicle received high safety ratings, including a five-star overall rating from the NHTSA. Spacious and Comfortable Interior: Reviewers and owners consistently praise the roomy cabin, offering significant headroom and legroom for a compact SUV. The seats are described as very comfortable, even for long trips. Excellent Visibility: The Forester's design, with slim pillars and large glass areas, provides outstanding all-around visibility, a significant safety benefit and driver convenience. Standard All-Wheel Drive and Off-Road Capability: Subaru's Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system is standard on all trims, not an optional extra as with many competitors. This, combined with 8.7 inches of ground clearance and X-Mode (standard on all but the base model), provides legitimate off-road capability for snow, dirt, and rough terrain. Generous Cargo Space: The vehicle offers a commodious 35.4 cubic feet of luggage space behind the rear seats (33.0 with the moonroof) and a maximum of 76.1 cubic feet with the rear seats folded, which is near the top of its class. It also features a wide rear gate opening for easy loading. High-End Amenities: As the top-of-the-line trim, the Touring comes with numerous premium features as standard, including: Perforated leather upholstery. Heated front and rear outboard seats. A heated steering wheel. An 8-inch infotainment system with navigation and a Harman Kardon premium audio system. Driver's seat and power mirror memory settings. Good Fuel Economy: The 2020 Forester is widely praised for its fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 26 city/33 highway MPG, which is competitive among all-wheel-drive compact SUVs. Durability and Reliability: The Forester has a strong reputation for durability and is built on a new platform designed for crashworthiness, quietness, and agility. This versatile SUV is perfect for families or contractors with its oversized cargo area, exceptional horsepower and option upgrades. Why spend more money than you have to? This Subaru Forester will help you keep the extra money you'd normally spend on gas. This AWD-equipped vehicle will handle beautifully on any terrain and in any weather condition your may find yourself in. The benefits of driving an all wheel drive vehicle, such as this Subaru Forester Touring, include superior acceleration, improved steering, and increased traction and stability. A Subaru with as few miles as this one is a rare find. This Forester Touring was gently driven and it shows. Added comfort with contemporary style is the leather interior to heighten the quality and craftsmanship for the Subaru Forester Touring. Performance, ease of use and efficiency are just a few reasons you'll love the navigation system that comes with this car.Accident or damage reported to Carfax

description: Conquer Every Terrain with the 2019 Ford F-150 Raptor: Power, Precision, and Performance in a Ruggedly Refined Package. Experience the thrill of the 2019 Ford F-150 Raptor, a used powerhouse designed for those who demand more from their drive. With its 3.5L V6 EcoBoost High Output engine and 10-speed automatic transmission, this truck delivers an exhilarating blend of power and efficiency, perfect for both off-road adventures and city cruising. The Raptor s 4x4 drivetrain and turbocharged performance ensure you can tackle any terrain with confidence, while the locking/limited slip differential provides superior traction control. The Oxford White exterior paired with aluminum wheels and all-terrain tires not only enhances its rugged appeal but also ensures durability in challenging conditions. Inside, the crew cab offers ample space with bucket seats and adjustable lumbar support for ultimate comfort on long journeys. Stay connected with smart device integration, Bluetooth connectivity, and a WiFi hotspot, making every drive both productive and enjoyable. Safety is paramount with features like front collision mitigation, automatic high beams, and a comprehensive airbag system. The Raptor s tow hooks and hitch make it ideal for hauling, while the rear parking aid and back-up camera ensure precision in tight spots. Drive the 2019 Ford F-150 Raptor and discover a new level of capability and comfort. Be sure to call or visit Van Hyundai to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

This 2021 Lincoln Corsair Standard is a premium compact SUV that offers exceptional style, performance, and technology. With its sleek exterior design, spacious interior, and advanced features, this Corsair is the perfect choice for the discerning driver.

• Convenience Package
• 18" Bright Machined Aluminum Wheels
• 17" Mini Spare Wheel

Under the hood, this Corsair is powered by a 2.0L I4 engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, delivering a smooth and efficient driving experience. With an EPA-estimated 22 MPG in the city and 29 MPG on the highway, you'll enjoy impressive fuel economy without sacrificing power.

The interior of the Corsair is equally impressive, with premium materials and thoughtful design touches throughout. The Convenience Package adds a host of desirable features, including a voice-activated touchscreen navigation system, universal garage door opener, ambient lighting, and a power liftgate for easy access to the spacious cargo area.

Comfort and convenience are prioritized in the Corsair, with heated front seats, a power driver's seat, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a premium audio system with SiriusXM radio. The 60/40 split-folding rear seats offer versatility, allowing you to accommodate passengers and cargo with ease.

Safety is also a top priority, with a suite of advanced driver-assist technologies, including automatic high-beam headlights, lane-keeping assist, and a rearview camera with dynamic parking lines. You can drive with confidence, knowing that you and your passengers are well-protected.

Whether you're commuting to the office, embarking on a weekend getaway, or tackling your daily errands, the 2021 Lincoln Corsair Standard is the perfect companion. The Rogue SV's impressive fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 28 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway, means you can go further on every tank, making it an ideal choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures. And with Nissan's legendary all-wheel-drive system, you can tackle any road with confidence, even in less-than-ideal weather conditions.

Step inside the Rogue SV and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed interior, complete with comfortable cloth seating, a versatile split-folding rear seat, and ample cargo space to accommodate your lifestyle. The thoughtful design and premium materials used throughout the cabin create an atmosphere of refined sophistication.

Safety is a top priority in the Rogue SV, which comes equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver assistance technologies. From automatic emergency braking and blind spot monitoring to rear parking sensors and a 360-degree camera system, you can drive with confidence, knowing you have a trusted co-pilot by your side.

Whether you're commuting to the office, embarking on a family road trip, or exploring the great outdoors, the 2023 Nissan Rogue SV is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology that this exceptional SUV has to offer. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Rogue SV is the ideal choice for your next vehicle.

description: The 2024 Nissan Sentra SV offers a modern blend of style, technology, and practicality, making it a standout choice for drivers seeking both comfort and confidence on the road. Powered by a fuel-efficient 2.0-liter engine, the Sentra SV delivers smooth acceleration and responsive handling, ideal for both city commuting and highway cruising. The sleek exterior design is complemented by clean lines and a refined stance, while the cabin offers a quiet, comfortable space with premium cloth seating and intuitive controls. With Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, drivers can easily access navigation, music, and messaging from their smartphones on the touchscreen display, keeping them connected and entertained on every journey.----Safety and convenience are at the forefront of the 2024 Sentra SV's design. Equipped with Adaptive Cruise Control, the vehicle automatically maintains a set distance from the car ahead, enhancing long-distance driving comfort. The Forward Collision Warning system adds an extra layer of protection by alerting the driver to potential frontal collisions, allowing precious seconds to react. Cross Traffic Alert and the Backup Camera work together to improve visibility and awareness when reversing, particularly in tight parking situations. These features, combined with Nissan's commitment to reliability, make the Sentra SV a smart, well-rounded option for drivers looking for advanced technology and dependable performance in a compact sedan.

Safety is paramount, and the Atlas Cross Sport delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver assistance technologies. Enjoy the peace of mind of features like ABS brakes, dual front impact and side airbags, electronic stability control, and the VW Car-Net Safe & Secure 5-year emergency communication system.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2025 Volkswagen Atlas Cross Sport 2.0T SE w/Technology. This exceptional SUV combines style, performance, and cutting-edge technology, making it the perfect companion for your next journey. Visit our showroom today and discover the difference for yourself.

description:
2025 PORSCHE 911 GT3 RS

WEISSACH PACKAGE, UNDER 1K MILES, FRONT AXLE LIFT, BOSE SOUND SYSTEM, AND MORE!

OVERVIEW
The 2025 Porsche 911 GT3 RS is the ultimate expression of Porsche's motorsport heritage, distilled into a street-legal supercar. And with the optional Weissach Package, this GT3 RS reaches another level of precision and it pushes the limits of what a naturally aspirated 911 can achieve. At its heart lies a 4.0-liter naturally aspirated flat-six engine, revving to a spine-tingling 9,000 rpm and producing 518 horsepower and 342 lb-ft of torque. Power in this GT3 RS is routed through a lightning-quick 7-speed PDK transmission. The result? 0-60 mph in just 3 seconds and a top speed of 184 mph. Aerodynamics play a starring role, with an aggressive rear diffuser and manually adjustable swan-neck rear wing that generate up to 150% more downforce than its predecessor. Agility is further enhanced by rear-axle steering and Porsche Active Suspension Management. From appearance alone, the GT3's wide body, center-lock wheels, and aggressive aero signal its intent without saying a word. Inside, this track-focused 911 remains modern and functional. Lightweight carbon bucket seats, Race-Tex trim throughout, and GT-specific driving modes provide a no-nonsense layout that keeps the focus firmly on driving. As with many Porsches, customization is key. This example features satin pyro red lightweight magnesium wheels, carbon fiber door sill guards, and a BOSE surround sound system. The 911 GT3 RS is more than just a road car. It's a precision tool for the track that's comfortable and refined enough to enjoy driving daily on the road. It's pure Porsche performance unfiltered.

description: The 2007 Ford Shelby GT500 Base is a high-performance muscle car that combines aggressive styling with remarkable power under the hood. Equipped with a supercharged 5.4-liter V8 engine producing 500 horsepower, this rear-wheel-drive coupe offers thrilling acceleration and a dynamic driving experience. The exterior is enhanced with bold design elements inspired by classic Shelby Mustangs, including racing stripes and a distinctive front grille. Fog lights improve visibility in low-light conditions and contribute to the car's assertive look on the road. The GT500 blends its heritage with modern driving features, making it a standout in the world of American performance cars.----Inside the cabin, the 2007 GT500 Base is outfitted with premium leather seats that add an upscale feel while providing excellent comfort during spirited drives. Both front seats are power-adjustable, ensuring customized seating for driver and passenger alike. Designed with safety in mind, the vehicle includes side impact airbags, offering added protection in the event of a collision. Keyless entry enhances convenience, allowing quick access without fumbling for keys. This combination of luxury and practicality brings everyday usability to a car that's otherwise known for its raw performance. Whether cruising on the highway or taking on winding roads, the 2007 Ford Shelby GT500 delivers excitement with a refined edge.

description: The 2018 Chevrolet Camaro SS is a high-performance muscle car that blends aggressive styling with modern technology and comfort. Under the hood, it features a powerful 6.2-liter V8 engine that delivers an exhilarating driving experience with 455 horsepower and 455 lb-ft of torque. This model is equipped with a Head Up Display that projects vital driving information directly onto the windshield, allowing drivers to stay focused on the road ahead. The premium leather seats offer both comfort and a touch of luxury, enhancing the overall driving environment. The Camaro SS offers a refined yet adrenaline-pumping ride suitable for both daily commutes and weekend adventures.----In addition to its performance and style, this Camaro is loaded with technology features to keep drivers connected and entertained. The built-in Wi-Fi Hotspot ensures seamless internet access for passengers, while the Premium Audio system delivers crystal-clear sound quality for an immersive listening experience. Navigation is seamlessly integrated into the infotainment system, providing turn-by-turn directions and real-time traffic updates. A sunroof adds another level of enjoyment, allowing natural light and fresh air into the cabin to enhance each drive. With its combination of power, luxury, and advanced tech features, the 2018 Chevrolet Camaro SS stands out as a modern take on the classic American muscle car.

Savor the performance of our One Owner 2024 Chevrolet Corvette Z06 3LZ Coupe that is engineered to exceed expectations on the track or off in Cacti Green! Powered by a 5.5 Liter High Output V8 serving up 670hp to a paddle-shifted 8 Speed Dual-Clutch Automatic transmission to help make the most of that muscle. A corner-carving Z06 suspension and Magnetic Selective Ride Control can lower your lap times even further, and this Rear Wheel Drive coupe sees nearly 21mpg on the highway. Our Corvette's stunning supercar silhouette grabs attention with LED lighting, bold alloy wheels, a rear spoiler, quad-center exhaust outlets, and a removable roof panel.

Stepping out in style, custom leather and microfiber trim enhance our 3LZ cockpit, which also boasts heated/ventilated GT2 leather power front seats with real carbon-fiber accents, a heated leather/carbon-fiber sport steering wheel, and dual-zone automatic climate control. Top tech benefits include a 12-inch driver display, an 8-inch touchscreen, Google Built-in compatibility, wireless Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, WiFi compatibility, connected navigation, a performance data recorder, and Bose Performance audio.

There's no need to sacrifice safety, either, since Chevrolet provides a digital rearview mirror, a head-up display, automatic braking, blind-spot monitoring, HD front/rear cameras, lane-keeping assistance, and more. Now let our Corvette Z06 3LZ welcome you to the winner's circle! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Grand Valley Auto Sales Test Drive Towards Ownership!

description: The 2023 Ford Expedition MAX Limited is the perfect combination of power, versatility, and modern luxury. As an extended-length SUV, it offers ample space for passengers and cargo, making it ideal for large families or those who frequently travel with extra gear. The exterior is bold and commanding, while inside, premium leather seats provide a refined and comfortable environment across all three rows. The third-row seating ensures that up to eight passengers can travel in style without compromising comfort. A panoramic sunroof stretches across the roofline, filling the spacious interior with natural light and giving all passengers an enhanced view of the surroundings.----Equipped with a host of advanced features, the 2023 Expedition MAX Limited brings convenience and safety to the forefront. Adaptive Cruise Control adjusts to traffic flow for a more relaxed driving experience, while Lane Keep Assist provides subtle steering inputs to help keep the vehicle centered on the road. Connectivity is also a strong suit, thanks to the built-in Wi-Fi hotspot that allows passengers to stay connected on the go. Whether you are heading out on a family road trip or navigating daily commutes, the Expedition MAX Limited delivers comfort, capability, and cutting-edge technology in a singular, spacious package.

Experience the power and capability of the 2024 Chevrolet Silverado 3500HD LT. This rugged and versatile truck is built to handle any task with ease, whether you're hauling heavy loads, towing a trailer, or navigating through challenging terrain.

Boasting a Duramax 6.6L V8 Turbodiesel engine, the Silverado 3500HD LT delivers an impressive 470 horsepower and an astounding 975 lb-ft of torque. Paired with a smooth-shifting 10-speed automatic transmission and a robust 4WD system, this truck is ready to tackle any job with confidence. Upgrade your driving experience with features like:

• Triton Certified Classic Vehicle
• 3 Month/4,000 Mile Comprehensive Warranty
• 6.6L V8 Diesel Turbocharged (Duramax) (B20-Diesel Compatible)
• ASSIST STEPS, CHROMED, 6" RECTANGULAR
• ALTERNATOR, 220 AMPS
• ENGINE BLOCK HEATER
• Preferred Equipment Group 1LT
• Suspension Package

The Silverado 3500HD LT also comes equipped with a host of premium features that elevate your driving experience, including SiriusXM with 360L, Bluetooth for phone connectivity, power windows and door locks, and a high-definition rear vision camera. With its spacious and well-appointed interior, this truck provides the perfect blend of capability and comfort.

This 2024 Chevrolet Silverado 3500HD LT is a Triton Certified vehicle, meaning it has undergone a rigorous inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty for your peace of mind. With low mileage and a clean CARFAX report, this truck is ready to take on your toughest tasks while providing a smooth and reliable ride.

Imagine the possibilities with this powerful and versatile Silverado 3500HD LT. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive today. Our knowledgeable sales team is here to answer any questions you may have and help you find the perfect truck to meet your needs.

Key features include:
• CRUISE CONTROL
• 6-Speed Automatic (PowerShift)
• Ruby Red Tinted Clearcoat
• Equipment Group 200A

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a host of premium amenities that enhance both comfort and convenience. Enjoy the convenience of the SYNC Communications & Entertainment System, along with steering wheel-mounted audio controls, power windows, and remote keyless entry. The spacious cabin and supportive cloth front bucket seats provide a relaxing environment, while the four-wheel independent suspension and electronic stability control deliver a confident, responsive ride.

Under the hood, the 2.0L 4-Cylinder DGI Flex Fuel DOHC engine, paired with a 6-Speed Automatic transmission, delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency. With an EPA-estimated 26 MPG in the city and 37 MPG on the highway, this Focus is designed to keep you moving with confidence.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, a knee airbag, and a comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies to help protect you and your passengers.

Whether you're commuting, running errands, or embarking on a weekend adventure, this 2014 Ford Focus SE is ready to exceed your expectations. Experience the perfect blend of style, technology, and efficiency – schedule a test drive today and discover the difference for yourself.

description:
Discover the versatility and convenience of the 2018 Ford Transit-150 XL. This capable cargo van is the perfect companion for your business or personal transportation needs. With its robust 3.7L V6 engine and rear-wheel-drive configuration, the Transit-150 delivers the power and handling you demand, whether navigating city streets or tackling long-haul deliveries.

Key features of this well-equipped model include:

• Bluetooth® connectivity for hands-free calling and audio streaming
• New tires for confident, all-weather performance
• Satellite radio for endless entertainment options
• USB ports for charging your devices on the go
• Backup camera for added safety and peace of mind

The thoughtfully designed interior of the Transit-150 XL provides the perfect blend of functionality and comfort. Enjoy the convenience of the SYNC® Communications and Entertainment System, complete with a 4-inch multi-function display, message center, and 6-speaker audio system. The leather-wrapped steering wheel with integrated controls puts all the essential features at your fingertips.

For added safety and security, this Transit-150 is equipped with a host of advanced features, including:

• Reverse Sensing System to assist with parking and maneuvering
• Cruise control with message center for effortless highway driving
• Heavy-duty 250-amp alternator to power your on-the-job equipment
• Daytime running lights for enhanced visibility

Whether you're transporting cargo, passengers, or a combination of both, the 2018 Ford Transit-150 XL is up to the task. Its versatile layout and ample cargo space make it the ideal choice for small businesses, tradespeople, or anyone in need of a hardworking, dependable van.

We invite you to experience the capabilities of this exceptional Transit-150 XL firsthand. Schedule a test drive today and discover how this van can elevate your daily driving and work-related tasks. Our team of knowledgeable sales professionals is here to assist you in finding the perfect solution to meet your unique needs.

What this vehicle includes:LX Technology Package ($500 value)Blind-Spot Collision-Avoidance AssistLane Change Assist6.5J X 16'''' Alloy WheelsRear Cross-Traffic Collision Avoidance AssistImmobilizer, Side Impact Beams, Dual Stage Driver And Passenger Seat-Mounted Side Airbags, Forward Collision-Avoidance Assist (fca), Collision Mitigation-Front, Driver Monitoring-Alert, Tire Specific Low Tire Pressure Warning, Dual Stage Driver And Passenger Front Airbags, Curtain 1st And 2nd Row Airbags, Airbag Occupancy Sensor, Back-Up CameraSafety and Security An active lane departure system alerts the driver of unintended movement of the vehicle out of a designated traffic lane and automatically maintains the vehicle's position within that lane. The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision. The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian. With this system the driver's hands must remain on the wheel at all times but can be removed briefly (for a few seconds), otherwise the vehicle will prompt the driver to put their hands back on the wheel.Technology and Telematics Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.SNOW WHITE PEARL, BLACK, WOVEN & TRICOT CLOTH SEAT TRIM, LX TECHNOLOGY PACKAGE, CARPETED FLOOR MATS Come on in to Cable Dahmer Kia of Lawrence today at 1225 E 23rd Street Lawrence KS 66046 or call 785-331-0016 to schedule a test drive!

This 2024 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited blends premium comfort with legendary capability, making it a standout choice for everyday driving and weekend adventures alike. With only 14,349 miles, this near-new SUV is polished, dependable, and ready to go.

Under the hood, you’ll find a powerful yet refined engine that delivers confident acceleration and smooth highway cruising. Inside, enjoy a spacious and quiet cabin filled with quality materials and thoughtful touches. The intuitive infotainment system with smartphone integration keeps you connected, while safety and driver-assist features help you feel confident behind the wheel.

At $36,991, this Grand Cherokee Limited represents tremendous value on a low-mile SUV that offers comfort, capability, and style in one versatile package.

The engine is paired with a smooth-shifting automatic transmission, providing both ease of use and the ability to unleash the car's full potential when desired.

This 1999 Plymouth Prowler comes equipped with a range of features designed to enhance your driving experience. Immerse yourself in the commanding luxury and cutting-edge innovation of the 2024 Mercedes-Benz GLS 450, a full-size SUV that redefines sophistication and performance. Finished in an exquisite Silver exterior, this CARFAX One-Owner, Accident-Free vehicle is a flawless example of Mercedes-Benz craftsmanship, blending dynamic presence with exceptional comfort. From city streets to open highways, the GLS 450 delivers a powerful and smooth driving experience, perfectly balanced by intelligent engineering and refined style. Step into a meticulously appointed cabin that showcases the finest materials and thoughtful design. The 7-seat configuration ensures ample space for passengers and cargo alike, while MB-Tex upholstery, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and heated and ventilated power front seats with memory create a tailored, first-class atmosphere for every occupant. The panoramic power moonroof opens the interior to the sky above, enhancing the sense of openness and connection with the road.

Every detail is crafted for comfort and convenience—from the steering wheel memory function to the fully automatic headlights and power liftgate, all designed to make daily driving effortless. Cutting-edge technology keeps you seamlessly connected, featuring MB Navigation, Apple CarPlay® and Android Auto®, SiriusXM radio, and a premium 13-speaker sound system that delivers rich, immersive audio throughout the cabin. For added confidence behind the wheel, an exterior parking camera enhances visibility and makes maneuvering in tight spaces a breeze.

On the outside, bold styling cues like the 21" triple 5-spoke wheels, elegant lines, and a distinctive rear spoiler underscore the vehicle’s commanding road presence. Whether you're driving across town or embarking on a weekend getaway, the 2024 GLS 450 offers the versatility of a luxury SUV with the prestige and performance that only Mercedes-Benz can deliver. This is more than just transportation—it’s a statement of excellence.

At Jack Ingram Motors, we’ve proudly delivered exceptional vehicles and service to the Southeast for over 60 years. Discover the pinnacle of refinement and innovation it’s time to love what you drive.

description:
Introducing the luxurious and powerful 2016 Chrysler 300 C. This sleek and stylish sedan is the epitome of sophistication and performance. With its spacious interior, advanced technology, and impressive features, the 300 C is the perfect choice for those who seek both comfort and class.

Under the hood, the 300 C boasts a 3.6-liter V6 engine, delivering a smooth and responsive ride. Its eight-speed automatic transmission allows for effortless shifting, while the available all-wheel drive provides added control and stability. Plus, with an impressive fuel efficiency of up to 31 MPG on the highway, the 300 C is not only powerful but also efficient.

Step inside and experience the ultimate in luxury. The 300 C's interior is adorned with premium materials, including Nappa leather-trimmed seats and real wood accents. The spacious cabin offers ample room for up to five passengers, making it ideal for long drives or daily commutes. And with features like heated and ventilated front seats, a panoramic sunroof, and a dual-zone automatic climate control, every journey will be a first-class experience.

The 300 C also comes equipped with the latest technology to keep you connected and entertained on the go. The Uconnect 8.4-inch touchscreen display allows for easy access to music, navigation, and hands-free calling. And with features like Bluetooth connectivity, SiriusXM satellite radio, and a premium sound system, you'll always stay connected and entertained.

But the 300 C isn't just about luxury and technology, it's also packed with advanced safety features to give you peace of mind on the road. From its available Forward Collision Warning with Active Braking to its Blind Spot Monitoring and Rear Cross-Path Detection, the 300 C is designed to keep you and your passengers safe.

Don't miss your chance to own the 2016 Chrysler 300 C. With its striking design, powerful performance, and top-of-the-line features, this sedan is sure to impress. Visit our showroom today and experience the luxury and sophistication of the 300 C for yourself.

Discover the perfect balance of performance, efficiency, and style with this 2017 Chevrolet Cruze LT. This sleek and sophisticated sedan is ready to take your driving experience to new heights.

• 6 Speaker Audio System Feature
• SiriusXM Satellite Radio
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Cloth Seat Trim
• 16" Aluminum Wheels

Under the hood, you'll find a powerful yet efficient 1.4L 4-Cylinder Turbo DOHC CVVT engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 6-Speed Automatic transmission and front-wheel drive. This combination delivers an impressive 30 city/40 highway MPG, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

The Cruze LT's interior is designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. Enjoy the convenience of remote keyless entry, steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and dual-zone climate control. Stay connected with the Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system, featuring a 7-inch touchscreen display, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto integration.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual front and side impact airbags, ABS brakes, electronic stability control, and a rear-view camera to give you peace of mind on the road.

This 2017 Chevrolet Cruze LT is the perfect blend of style, performance, and practicality. With its sleek exterior, well-appointed interior, and impressive fuel efficiency, it's the ideal choice for the discerning driver. Visit our showroom today to experience the Cruze LT for yourself and discover why it should be your next vehicle.

Certification Program Details: Multi-Point Inspection: Each certified vehicle undergoes a 126-point inspection conducted by trained technicians. This covers engine performance, brakes, tires, suspension, safety systems, and more. Vehicle History Report: A free CARFAX® or AutoCheck® report is provided, ensuring transparency on previous ownership, accident history, title status, etc. Limited Warranty Coverage: 6-month/6,000-mile limited warranty (whichever comes first), covering major systems and components. Roadside Assistance: 24/7 roadside assistance is included during the warranty period. Courtesy Transportation: If your car is in the shop for a covered repair, you get courtesy transportation or reimbursement. OnStar® and SiriusXM® Trials: Many certified vehicles include OnStar and SiriusXM trials (usually 3 months), when equipped. Return Policy: Some vehicles may come with a 7-day or 150-mile exchange policy, depending on the dealership. Digital Tools and Convenience: Online shopping tools, home delivery (at participating dealers), and trade-in options make the process more convenient.

We would love the opportunity to keep giving the best values in the market. description: The 2023 Toyota GR86 Base is a spirited and agile sports coupe designed to deliver an exhilarating driving experience with modern convenience features. Built with performance in mind, this rear-wheel-drive coupe boasts a responsive 2.4-liter 4-cylinder engine paired with a lightweight chassis, offering sharp handling and dynamic acceleration. The model features a sleek, aerodynamic exterior, enhanced with a unique Special Color finish and a Black Rear Bumper Applique that adds a touch of aggressive styling to its already athletic stance. Designed to meet emissions standards across the country, the GR86 includes 50 State Emissions compliance, making it a smart choice for performance enthusiasts nationwide.----Inside, the 2023 GR86 Base balances its driver-focused cockpit with cutting-edge technology and comfort. Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility allow seamless smartphone integration, keeping music, navigation, and communication effortlessly accessible through the touchscreen display. A Backup Camera adds convenience and confidence when reversing or parking, while Bluetooth connectivity keeps drivers connected without distractions. The Automatic Climate Control system maintains the perfect cabin temperature without the need for manual adjustments, and the Push Start feature adds ease of access, letting you start the engine with the touch of a button. With a focus on both performance and everyday usability, the GR86 delivers a well-rounded package fit for weekend thrill-seekers and daily commuters alike.

This 2023 GMC Yukon XL SLT is a true standout in the full-size SUV segment, offering an unparalleled blend of power, versatility, and premium features. With its spacious interior, advanced technology, and commanding presence on the road, this Yukon XL is the perfect companion for your family adventures and everyday driving needs.

The advanced technology features, including Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and a Bose premium audio system, keep you connected and entertained on the go.

Whether you're hauling the family, towing a boat, or embarking on a road trip, this 2023 GMC Yukon XL SLT is the perfect companion. With its impressive capabilities, premium amenities, and timeless style, it's a vehicle that will exceed your expectations and make every journey a pleasure.

description: The 2025 Dodge Durango R/T is a powerful and versatile SUV that blends aggressive performance with cutting-edge technology and family-friendly comfort. Under the hood, the Durango R/T boasts a muscular V8 engine that delivers thrilling acceleration and a confident driving experience, whether you're navigating city streets or heading out on a weekend road trip. The vehicle comes equipped with a Third Row Seat, allowing for seating up to seven passengers, making it perfect for larger families or anyone who needs extra space. With a bold exterior design and refined interior craftsmanship, the Durango R/T perfectly balances ruggedness with refinement.----Inside, the 2025 Durango R/T is packed with tech-savvy features to keep everyone connected and entertained. A built-in Wi-Fi Hotspot ensures internet access on the go, while premium audio elevates every playlist, podcast, or call with crystal-clear sound. The intuitive Navigation system provides real-time guidance and traffic updates, making every journey smoother. Seamless smartphone integration with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto makes it easy to access apps, music, messages, and more, all through the vehicle's user-friendly infotainment system. Whether you're commuting, carpooling, or embarking on a cross-country adventure, the 2025 Dodge Durango R/T delivers a dynamic driving experience and the modern amenities today's drivers demand.

description:
Theres a gladiatorial grace to the 2021 Jaguar FPACE SVRan animal in tailored armor that manages to be both urbane and unapologetically feral. From a distance it reads like a sculpted predator poised at the edge of civility: broad haunches, flared wheel arches and a low, prowlike nose that suggests motion even when the engine is quiet. The SVRs exterior is all purposeful punctuationair intakes that look functional by conviction, a roofline that slopes like a coupes compromise, and quad exhaust outlets that insist on being noticed. Its an SUV with theatrical instincts, wearing performance details as if they were bespoke cufflinks.

Slide into the cabin and the dual personality becomes tactile. The cockpit wraps you in a satisfying mix of luxury and restraint: deep, bolstered seats that bracket the driver, stitched leather and alcantara that invite touch, and carbon accents that whisper of track days without shouting. The controls are arranged with an almost clubby logicswitches and paddles that feel weighted and decisiveand the interiors palette balances warmth and purpose so that every surface rewards attention rather than glare.

On the road the FPACE SVR is pure temperament translated into motion. Theres an immediacy to its responses that delights: steering with a direct, communicative edge, a chassis that resists theatrical body roll and instead channels momentum with composed aggression, and a ride that can soothe a boulevard or sharpen on a canyon run. Its not a blunt instrument, its a precise oneable to hustle down an onramp with theatrical urgency and then settle into a velvety, composed stride for long stretches. The driving experience feels intentionally cinematic: moments of visceral excitement punctuate long chapters of cultivated refinement.

Sound design is part of the character. The exhaust doesnt merely announce acceleration, it performs, swelling with a low, throaty authority and occasionally popping like punctuation when the throttle is eased. Inside, the cabin balances that aural drama with isolation where conversation matters, creating a sense that the car knows when to sing and when to listen.

Practical comforts are honest and consideredroom for passengers and luggage exists, but never as an afterthought. Technology and creature comforts integrate in service of the drive: helpful, present, and not insistent. In short, the 2021 FPACE SVR is a study in contrasts: sumptuous and savage, civilized and ready to pounce. Its for the driver who wants an SUV that behaves like a performance car most of the timeand like a showpiece every time the road invites a bit of mischief.

Step inside the Envista and be greeted by the refined Leatherette seating, 8-way power driver's seat, and heated steering wheel. The Watts Link System Rear Suspension delivers a smooth and responsive ride, while the power moonroof allows you to bask in the natural beauty of the outdoors.

*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height) min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]'' tabindex=''-1'' dir=''auto'' data-turn-id=''request-WEB:b3e9da97-1105-4c13-9e85-4fdecfda9986-8'' data-testid=''conversation-turn-18'' data-scroll-anchor=''true'' data-turn=''assistant''> 2023 Kia Telluride S — Rugged Style Meets Everyday Capability Introducing the 2023 Kia Telluride S — a bold, versatile SUV that delivers practical performance, spacious comfort, and intelligent design in a package built for modern lifestyles. The S trim strikes the perfect balance between capability and value, offering thoughtful features and confident presence without compromise. Powered by a responsive 3.8-liter V6 engine paired with a smooth-shifting automatic transmission, the Telluride S delivers balanced performance for daily driving, highway cruising, and weekend adventures alike. Confident handling and a well-tuned suspension ensure a composed ride, while available all-wheel drive enhances traction and confidence in changing conditions. On the outside, the Telluride S stands out with its rugged yet refined design — bold grille, athletic stance, and distinctive LED lighting give it a commanding road presence. The strong profile and purposeful lines reflect Telluride’s capability-ready character, perfect for family outings, road trips, or everyday errands. Step inside the spacious cabin and discover an interior that’s both comfortable and functional. With three rows of seating and generous passenger room, the Telluride S accommodates families and cargo with ease. description:
This 2023 Ford Bronco Black Diamond 2-Door in Iconic Silver Metallic offers rugged off-road capability wrapped in a modern, versatile package, powered by a 2.3L EcoBoost I-4 engine with a 4.46 final drive ratio and rear locking differential. Ford Gold Certified and featuring a Clean CARFAX, it comes equipped with the 322A Mid Package, front-row heated marine-grade vinyl bucket seats, dual-zone electronic climate control, and ambient footwell lighting. The Carbonized Gray molded-in-color hard top with sound-deadening headliner and integrated roll-over protection enhances comfort and safety, while 17" black gloss-painted steel wheels complete its bold, trail-ready look.

Tech and convenience are fully loaded with Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, connected navigation, exterior parking camera, rear parking sensors, remote start, remote keyless entry, power windows and mirrors, and a rear-window defroster with washer. Additional safety features include ABS brakes, traction control, low tire pressure warning, and electronic stability control. Backed by Ford Gold Certification, including an 84-month/100,000-mile powertrain limited warranty, 172-point inspection, roadside assistance, and 22,000 FordPass Rewards Points, this Bronco is ready for adventure. Available now at AutoFair Ford of Manchester, New Hampshirethe #1 Ford Certified and used Ford dealer in New England, serving Concord, Nashua, Salem, Londonderry, Laconia, Rochester, and Exeter. See more at autofairford.com.

The versatile split-folding rear seat and generous cargo space make this sedan an excellent choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

This 2023 Toyota Camry LE has been meticulously inspected and certified, ensuring that it meets the highest standards of quality and reliability. With low mileage and a clean CARFAX report, this vehicle is a true gem that offers exceptional value.

Experience power and refinement with this 2022 Ram 2500 Limited 4WD, now available in Corinth, MS. Powered by a robust 6-cylinder, 6.7L diesel engine, this heavy-duty truck delivers exceptional towing capability, impressive torque, and long-haul efficiency. The Limited trim combines luxury and utility with upscale leather appointments, advanced tech, and durable construction built for work and weekend adventures. Safety and convenience features include Adaptive Cruise Control for confident highway driving, a Back-Up Camera for precise maneuvering, and Hands-Free Bluetooth for connected, distraction-free calls. Enjoy crisp audio through the Premium Sound System during every drive. This vehicle also comes with a CARFAX Clean Report, offering verified history and added peace of mind. Comfort-focused amenities and thoughtful technology make the cab a productive and relaxing space. Four-wheel drive enhances traction across varied road conditions, while the diesel powertrain provides durable performance and towing strength for trailers, boats, and heavy loads. This 2022 Ram 2500 Limited is competitively priced and represents the best price in the area — a compelling value for buyers seeking premium capability without compromise. Located in Corinth, MS, this truck is ready for a test drive. Contact us to schedule an appointment and experience the blend of power, luxury, and reliability this Ram 2500 Limited offers.

Equipment
This three-quarter ton truck can tow almost anything. When you encounter slick or muddy roads, you can engage the four wheel drive on the vehicle and drive with confidence. It has automated speed control that adjusts to maintain a safe following distance, enhancing highway driving convenience. This Ram 2500 offers Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration. This unit offers Apple CarPlay for seamless connectivity. Protect this 3/4 ton pickup from unwanted accidents with a cutting edge backup camera system. The Ram 2500 has an elegant black exterior finish. Our dealership has already run the CARFAX report and it is clean. A clean CARFAX is a great asset for resale value in the future. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in this 2022 Ram 2500 is easy with the climate control system. Easily set your speed in this 3/4 ton pickup with a state of the art cruise control system. Increase or decrease velocity with the touch of a button. With a diesel engine you will be pleased with the power, torque, and fuel efficiency gains. This 3/4 ton pickup has a 6 Cyl, 6.7L high output engine. This vehicle's Forward Collision Warning feature alerts drivers to potential front-end collisions. Bluetooth technology is built into this 3/4 ton pickup, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. This unit is pure luxury with a heated steering wheel. Quickly unlock it with keyless entry. This 2022 Ram 2500 stays safely in its lane with Lane Keep Assist. The leather seats in this 3/4 ton pickup are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. With the adjustable lumbar support in the vehicle your back will love you. The installed navigation system will keep you on the right path. This 2022 Ram 2500 has a premium sound system installed. Start the vehicle from inside with remote start. A trailer braking system is already installed on this unit. with XM/Sirus Satellite Radio you are no longer restricted by poor quality local radio stations while driving this model. Anywhere on the planet, you will have hundreds of digital stations to choose from.Bluetooth technology is built into this 3/4 ton pickup, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road.

Outfitted with a factory lift, off-road suspension, and aggressive styling, the LT Trail Boss trim stands out with its bold exterior and trail-ready performance. The backup camera enhances safety during parking and tight maneuvers, while automatic climate control maintains a comfortable cabin environment no matter the weather. Whether you're commuting or heading off-road, the Silverado LT Trail Boss combines confidence-inspiring capability with the tech-savvy features today's drivers demand.

description: Discover the rugged versatility and dependable performance of this 2021 Toyota 4Runner SR5 SUV, now available as a used vehicle. Boasting a striking Blueprint exterior complemented by a comfortable Gray interior, this 4WD-equipped SUV is built for adventure and daily driving alike. With a robust 4.0-liter V6 engine delivering 270 horsepower and 278 lb-ft of torque, it offers impressive capability and reliable power. Its 5-speed automatic transmission ensures smooth shifts, while the 191,557 miles reflect a well-maintained legacy of durability. Designed with practicality in mind, this 4Runner features four doors and seating for five, making it an ideal choice for families or outdoor enthusiasts. Modern amenities such as Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth connectivity, a backup camera, and a satellite radio ready system enhance your driving experience, while safety features like collision warning and adaptive cruise control provide peace of mind on every journey. The inclusion of a tow package and Wifi hotspot further elevates its versatility, making it suitable for both work and play. This 2021 Toyota 4Runner SR5 combines rugged capability with advanced technology, ensuring you're connected and protected on every adventure. The vehicle is equipped with a comprehensive suite of safety features, including dual front knee airbags and active head restraints to safeguard occupants. Four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS) and auto-locking power door locks add security and stability, while hill descent control assists with off-road driving, giving you confidence in challenging terrains. Whether tackling city streets or exploring off-road trails, this SUV offers a reliable and secure driving experience, backed by Toyota's renowned safety standards. 2021 Toyota 4Runner Safety and Security Features This model is equipped with essential safety features such as dual front knee airbags and active head restraints to protect occupants in the event of a collision. The four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS) provides enhanced stopping power, especially in emergency situations. Auto-locking power door locks ensure added security when the vehicle is parked, while off-road driving assist with hill descent control helps maintain control during challenging terrains, making it an excellent choice for adventurous drivers seeking peace of mind. 2021 Toyota 4Runner Entertainment and Technology Features The 4Runner SR5 offers a suite of modern entertainment and connectivity options, including Toyota Connected Services for smart device app compatibility. Hands-free voice-operated phone call integration and a voice-operated radio system keep you connected safely while on the road. An 8-inch infotainment touchscreen with touch controls, complemented by eight speakers, delivers clear audio and easy access to your favorite media. Amazon Alexa compatibility allows for seamless voice commands, while electronic messaging assistance with a read function and voice operation enhances convenience. The system also features auxiliary USB audio input, ensuring you stay entertained and connected during every journey. 2021 Toyota 4Runner Performance Features Performance-wise, this 4Runner is built for both on-road comfort and off-road capability. It features an electronic hi-lo 4WD selector, allowing drivers to switch between high and low-range gearing for optimal traction in diverse conditions. The part-time 4WD system provides control and stability, making it a reliable partner whether you're navigating city streets or tackling rugged trails.

description: The 2020 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a thrilling fusion of iconic design and exhilarating performance. Its sleek, sculpted exterior turns heads with timeless elegance and dynamic presence. The powerful twin-turbo flat-six engine delivers immediate acceleration and refined power at every speed. All-wheel drive provides exceptional traction and confidence in varied driving conditions. The engines response feels sharp and engaging, making every journey exciting. Precision steering creates a direct connection between driver and road. The suspension balances agility and comfort, adapting effortlessly to twists and straights. Braking performance is strong, consistent, and reassuring in spirited driving. The Carrera 4S feels composed and poised through corners with remarkable grip. Inside, the cabin blends luxury and sport-focused design beautifully. Premium materials create an atmosphere of refinement and quality. Sport seats provide excellent support and comfort for both driver and passenger. The driver-oriented cockpit enhances focus and engagement behind the wheel. Intuitive controls are placed for effortless operation at speed or in traffic. The infotainment system is responsive, modern, and easy to navigate. A crisp, high-resolution display keeps essential information clearly visible. Smartphone connectivity is seamless for music, navigation, and communication. A premium sound system fills the cabin with rich, immersive audio. Climate controls maintain a pleasant environment for all occupants. The Carrera 4S offers generous storage for a sports car, perfect for weekend getaways. Visibility is excellent, enhancing confidence and enjoyment on every drive. The athletic stance and distinctive details reflect Porsches racing heritage. The exhaust note is powerful and exhilarating, adding to the driving experience. Every curve and line reflects meticulous craftsmanship. Advanced technology works smoothly to enhance both comfort and performance. The 911s legendary build quality radiates confidence and durability. The overall driving experience is exhilarating, refined, and endlessly engaging. The 2020 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S stands as a pinnacle of sports car excellence. Each moment behind the wheel feels connected, joyful, and unforgettable. This 911 delivers pure performance with uncompromising luxury and style.911 Carrera 4S, 2D Coupe, 3.0L H6 Turbocharged DOHC 24V LEV3-ULEV70 443hp, 8-Speed Porsche Doppelkupplung (PDK), AWD, Carrara White Metallic, Black Leather. This outstanding example of a 2017 Chevrolet Tahoe LS is offered by AutoNation Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram Houston. This Chevrolet includes: ENGINE, 5.3L ECOTEC3 V8 WITH ACTIVE FUEL MANAGEMENT, DIRECT INJECTION AND VARIABLE VALVE TIMINGFlex Fuel Capability 8 Cylinder Engine *Note - For third party subscriptions or services, please contact the dealer for more information.*With this exceptional SUV, you'll get "sport," "utility," and comfort. Put performance, safety, beauty, sophistication and all the right amenities into a car, and here it is! Now you can own luxury without the luxury price tag!More information about the 2017 Chevrolet Tahoe:The Suburban and Tahoe are by far the best-selling models in their class, and they're tough rivals for the Ford Expedition, Toyota Sequoia and Nissan Armada, among others. These two Chevy models are closely related in most ways--although there's a key difference: the Suburban is 14 inches longer in wheelbase and 20 inches longer overall than the Tahoe, and that results in a significantly larger third-row seat than in the Tahoe--as well as easier access to it, and more cargo space. Compared to rival models, the Chevy Tahoe and Suburban stand out for their ride quality and relatively efficient engines. They're also very rugged and versatile, and can be outfitted for off-road toughness, tow ability and interior luxury as needed. Chevrolet claims that the Suburban will be the most fuel-efficient model in the full-size SUV class, thanks to tech such as direct injection and active fuel management (cylinder deactivation). Although the profile of the Suburban and Tahoe haven't changed all that much, Chevy has managed to make significant improvements to aerodynamics. Chiseled sheet metal and big, flamboyant wheels (up to 22 inches) help maintain a powerful look.Interesting features of this model are Much-improved interior, seating space, towing ability, versatility and toughness, comfortable, refined ride, and relatively fuel-efficient engines

description:
2018 Dodge Challenger SRT Demon $109,000This 2018 Dodge Challenger SRT Demon was professionally built, serviced, and maintained by the same performance shop throughout its life. The car was used primarily for marketing, dyno calibration, and validation, not neglected or abused. It has a well-documented service and modification history, with dyno sheets and receipts on hand.This is a rare Demon that delivers true street manners while still being fully capable as a serious weekend race car.POWER & PERFORMANCE
  • 950 HP on 93 octane (767 RWHP)
  • 1,200 HP on E85 (1,064 RWHP) Link to post
  • Professional engine and transmission calibration
MODIFICATIONS & UPGRADES (DOCUMENTED)Engine & Power
  • Hellion compound boost twin turbo system
  • Dual 64/66R V-band turbochargers
  • Blower-delete configuration
  • Injector Dynamics IDX 1300 fuel injectors
  • JMS FuelMAX V2 fuel pump voltage booster
  • HP Tuners MPVI3 with engine & transmission licensing
  • Dodge PCM unlock & Smart Access Cable
  • Custom dyno and street tuning
  • 93 octane calibration
  • E85 calibration
Drivetrain
  • Pure Drivetrain Solutions ZF 8HP95 transmission upgrade
  • Upgraded race torque converter
  • Transmission professionally removed, upgraded, and reinstalled
Wheels, Tires & Chassis
  • Factory Demon wheels included
  • Optional drag pack available for an additional fee
  • Weld RTS-82 beadlock wheels
  • 18x5 front
  • 15x11 rear
  • Mickey Thompson ET Street R rear tires
  • Mickey Thompson Sportsman S/R front tires
  • Carlyle Racing 15 rear brake conversion
  • BWoody rear differential brace
DAILY DRIVER + WEEKEND RACERDespite its power level, this Demon remains comfortable, streetable, and easy to drive, making it a legitimate daily driver if desired. When equipped with the optional drag pack, it quickly transitions into a track-ready setup with no compromises.DOCUMENTATION & HISTORY
  • Over $50,000+ in documented performance modifications
  • Dyno sheets available
  • Receipts and invoices on hand
  • Maintained by the same shop that built it
WHY THIS DEMON STANDS OUTThis is not a rushed or pieced-together build. Every modification was selected, installed, tuned, and maintained with long-term reliability and performance in mind. No guesswork, no unfinished work just a proven, dialed-in Demon.

2018 Dodge Challenger SRT Demon

Pitch Black Clearcoat | One-Year-Only Production

The 2018 Dodge Challenger SRT Demon is a factory-built, drag-strip-dominating muscle car produced for one model year only, making it one of the most collectible modern Dodges ever built. Finished in Pitch Black Clearcoat, this Demon delivers an aggressive, sinister look that perfectly matches its extreme performance pedigree.

Powered by a supercharged 6.2L HEMI® V8, the Demon was engineered specifically for straight-line performance and is capable of 0–60 mph in as little as 2.3 seconds with the proper setup. Every Demon came equipped with specialized drag hardware, unique calibration, and track-focused engineering straight from the factory.

Performance & Engineering

Supercharged 6.2L HEMI® V8

Drag-focused suspension tuning

Widebody stance with flared fenders

Air-Grabber™ hood for maximum airflow

Nitto NT05R drag radial tires

Lightweight components and weight-reduction features

Designed for quarter-mile dominance

Interior & Comfort (Customer Preferred Package 26M)

Laguna leather/Alcantara® Demon logo performance seats

Front passenger seat installed

Heated and ventilated front seats

Heated steering wheel

Power tilt and telescoping steering column

Bright pedals

Premium floor mats

Leather rear seat with 60/40 split folding functionality

Rear armrest with integrated cup holders

Child seat tether anchors

Exclusivity & Collectibility

One-year-only production (2018 model year)

Iconic Pitch Black exterior finish

Factory Demon Crate–equipped model

Purpose-built from the factory as a street-legal drag car

Highly sought after by collectors and enthusiasts

The 2018 Challenger SRT Demon is not just a muscle car—it’s a milestone in automotive performance history. Purpose-built, brutally fast, and increasingly rare, this Demon represents one of the most extreme factory vehicles ever offered to the public.

Experience the thrill of driving with this stunning 2018 Porsche 911 GT3 Coupe, a masterpiece in automotive engineering and design. Cloaked in an exquisite GT Silver Metallic finish, this sports car is powered by a formidable 4.0L 6-cylinder engine delivering an exhilarating 500 horsepower and 339 lb-ft of torque. The precision of its 6-speed manual transmission ensures every drive is as engaging as it is powerful, making it perfect for those who crave performance and control.
Inside, luxury meets technology with premium leather seats that are heated for your comfort. Stay connected effortlessly through Bluetooth connectivity while navigating seamlessly using the advanced navigation system. For added convenience, features like a backup camera ensure safety without compromising on style or functionality. This low-mileage gem has only traveled 8,365 miles and comes equipped with an entertainment system to enhance every journey.
Important: This GT3 received a branded title approximately five years ago. Since that time, the vehicle has undergone consistent inspections and has been meticulously maintained, resulting in a car that drives, looks, and performs exactly as it should. It is absolutely dialed in today—which is why this represents an opportunity to own a GT3 at a significantly lower price point than comparable examples on the market.

Intermittent Wipers The Ferrari 296 GTB is special for several revolutionary reasons, primarily because it marks a significant shift in Ferrari&#39,s core sports car philosophy by introducing a new V6 plug-in hybrid (PHEV) powertrain. Here are the most special and unique aspects of the 296 GTB:1. The Revolutionary V6 Hybrid PowertrainThis is the most significant feature and a first for a mainline Ferrari model:First V6 for a Production Ferrari (Since the Dino): It&#39,s the first road car to wear the Ferrari badge that uses a V6 engine since the legendary Dino models of the 60s and 70s (which were marketed as a separate brand). The &quot,Hot-V&quot, Engine Design: The all-new twin-turbo V6 has its turbochargers mounted inside the &quot,V&quot, of the cylinder banks. This &quot,hot-vee&quot, configuration: Increases compactness and lowers the engine&#39,s center of gravity.Achieves a world-record-setting specific power output of hp per liter for a production car. Plug-in Hybrid (PHEV) System: The V6 is paired with a rear-mounted electric motor (MGU-K) to deliver a massive combined output of 819 hp (830 cv), which is sent exclusively to the rear wheels. Electric-Only Driving: The PHEV system allows for a short electric-only range (around miles / km) at speeds up to mph, enabling silent running through urban &quot,zero-emission zones.&quot, 2. Aerodynamic Innovation &amp, DesignThe car&#39,s design is heavily influenced by aerodynamics and features a shorter wheelbase for enhanced agility: Active Downforce: Unlike previous Ferrari active aero systems that primarily managed drag, the 296 GTB uses a LaFerrari-inspired active rear spoiler that deploys to generate additional downforce (up to kg with the Assetto Fiorano package). Compact, Sculpted Design: The car has a shorter wheelbase than previous mid-rear-engined V8 Ferraris (like the F8 Tributo), which enhances its agility and gives it a highly compact, monolithic appearance. Tribute to the Past: Its simple, beautiful forms and side air intakes reference classic Ferraris, most notably the iconic 1963 250 LM race car.3. Focus on &quot,Fun to Drive&quot,Ferrari engineered the 296 GTB to deliver a highly engaging and usable driving experience, which they call &quot,fun-to-drive&quot,:New Dynamic Controls: It features a world-first 6-way Chassis Dynamic Sensor (6w-CDS), a new ABS evo controller, and electric power steering, all working together to improve handling and braking performance. Soundtrack of a V12: The V6 engine was meticulously tuned, earning the nickname &quot,piccolo V12&quot, (little V12), as its configuration and high rpm redline allow it to reproduce the pure, high-frequency notes of a naturally aspirated V12 engine.In short, the Ferrari 296 GTB is special because it is a PHEV V6 revolution that ushers in a new era of performance and technology for Ferrari while retaining and elevating the brand&#39,s core values of agility and driving emotion.

With its powerful 3.8L 6-cylinder turbocharged engine and lightning-fast 7-speed Porsche Doppelkupplung (PDK) transmission, this all-wheel-drive sports car delivers an exhilarating driving experience like no other.Boasting an impressive array of premium features, this Turbo S is equipped with:Navigation System13-Speaker Audio SystemPorsche Communication ManagementAdaptive Sport Seats with Driver MemoryPower Comfort Seats with Driver MemoryFull Leather Seat TrimBi-Xenon Headlights with CleaningRear Fog LightsAdaptive SuspensionCeramic Disc BrakesPower MoonroofHeated and Auto-Dimming MirrorsHomeLink Garage Door OpenerRain-Sensing WipersFinished in a striking Meteor exterior color, this 911 Turbo S exudes a bold, sophisticated presence that is sure to turn heads wherever you go. With its low mileage of just 46,565, this exceptional sports car has been meticulously serviced and is ready to provide you with an unparalleled driving experience.Slip behind the wheel of this Porsche masterpiece and feel the power and precision that have made the 911 a global icon. The Turbo S's seamless acceleration, razor-sharp handling, and impeccable build quality will leave you in awe. Whether carving through twisty roads or effortlessly cruising the highway, this Porsche will deliver an unmatched level of performance and driving enjoyment.Owning a 911 Turbo S is a privilege that few can experience. This is your opportunity to join the elite ranks of Porsche enthusiasts and become the proud owner of a true automotive legend. Schedule a test drive today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional sports car can elevate your driving experience to new heights.

description:
Motorcars of the Main Line is proud to present this 2014 Porsche 911 50th Anniversary Edition --- 1 of 1,963 Worldwide, Highly Optioned, Exceptional ConditionVIN: WP0AB2A97ES121398
Mileage: 24,608 miles
Exterior Color: Graphite Grey
Interior Color: Leather Interior in Black
History: Clean Carfax | Collector-Owned | (Porsche Certified Pre-Owned) Overview This 2014 Porsche 911 50th Anniversary Edition celebrates fifty years of the legendary 911 with a perfect balance of heritage and modern performance. Finished in Graphite Grey over Black Leather, this example is one of just 1,963 produced globally. Built on the Carrera S platform and powered by the 3.8L flat-six engine paired with Porsche's lightning-fast PDK transmission, the 50th Anniversary Edition is distinguished by exclusive styling cues, unique badging, Fuchs-inspired wheels, and bespoke trim details. With only 24,608 miles, this example is a pristine and collectible representation of Porsche history. Factory Options & Highlights
  • Porsche Doppelkupplung (PDK) --- 7-speed dual-clutch transmission
  • Limitation Number --- individually numbered, 1 of 1,963 worldwide
  • Seat Heating (Front)
  • Seat Ventilation (Front)
  • Adaptive Cruise Control including Porsche Active Safe (PAS)
  • LED Headlights including Porsche Dynamic Light System Plus (PDLS+)
  • Porsche Entry & Drive
  • ParkAssist (Front and Rear)
  • Electric Sunroof
  • Power Steering Plus
  • BOSE Surround Sound System
  • SiriusXM Satellite Radio Receiver
  • Multifunction Steering Wheel
  • Adaptive Sport Seats Plus (18-way)
  • Fuel Cap with Aluminum Look Finish
  • Ornamental Porsche Crest
Performance & Specifications
  • 3.8L Flat-6 Engine --- 400 horsepower/325 lb-ft torque
  • 7-Speed Porsche Doppelkupplung (PDK)
  • Rear-Wheel Drive
  • 0--60 mph in approximately 4.2 seconds
  • Top speed: 186 mph
  • Exclusive 50th Anniversary Styling --- Fuchs-style wheels, chrome trim, wider rear body, and unique "911 50" badging
Why Buy From Motorcars of the Main Line
  • Enthusiast-owned dealership specializing in premium, performance, and collector-grade vehicles
  • Concierge nationwide and international shipping
  • Transparent listings with professional photography and detailed descriptions
Additional Information
  • Shipping to your location is not a problem --- we have clients all over the world and can arrange secure delivery to your door.
  • We are a licensed Pennsylvania Tag Issuing Agent offering all tag and title services, including temporary and transit plates. We also handle tag and title work for all 50 states.
  • We welcome trade-ins of all makes & models. Financing for qualified buyers is available.
  • We encourage you to call with any questions or concerns, no matter how small. Many of our ads end early with a simple phone call.
Visit us: www.mcotml.com
Showroom: Motorcars of the Main Line, 378 Crooked Ln #3, King of Prussia, PA 19406
Contact: sales@mcotml.com | 484-612-4147

description: The 2019 Porsche 911 Carrera T delivers a thrilling driving experience with its iconic design and outstanding performance capabilities. Built for driving enthusiasts, the Carrera T features a rear-mounted 3.0-liter twin-turbocharged flat-six engine, delivering 370 horsepower through a precision-tuned rear-wheel-drive system. Designed with a focus on lightweight materials and performance enhancements, this model offers a purist approach with sharper handling and a lower ride height compared to the standard Carrera. With distinct sporty accents like an exclusive front lip spoiler and unique badging, the Carrera T maintains the timeless look of the 911 while offering a more dynamic edge, perfect for those seeking the pure essence of a classic sports car.----Beyond performance, this 911 Carrera T comes equipped with modern convenience and technology features that enhance everyday usability. A built-in Wi-Fi Hotspot keeps passengers connected on the go, while the integrated navigation system ensures precision guidance wherever the road leads. Apple CarPlay integration allows seamless connection of a compatible iPhone, bringing familiar apps and functionality to the intuitive infotainment system. Xenon headlights provide crisp and bright illumination for improved road visibility, and an advanced backup camera assists with parking and maneuvering in tight spaces. Additionally, automatic climate control ensures a consistently comfortable cabin environment, adjusting to maintain ideal temperatures no matter the outside conditions. With the perfect blend of performance heritage and modern technology, the 2019 Porsche 911 Carrera T is a formidable choice for those who value both driving excitement and daily comfort.

Exceptionally low mileage — under 6,000 miles (averaging less than 1,000 miles per year) — and in excellent overall condition. Factory-equipped with an 8-speed dual-clutch transmission and all-wheel drive, handcrafted leather and real wood veneer trim, power-adjustable heated front seats with memory, dual-zone automatic climate control, multifunction leather steering wheel, adaptive suspension with selectable drive modes, premium audio and integrated navigation, Bluetooth connectivity, xenon headlights with LED daytime running lights, parking sensors and rearview camera, full airbag suite, ABS, traction and stability control, keyless entry and push-button start. The ultimate Autobahn luxury cruiser with 5K Miles ! The Continental GT is more about luxury and style than tearing up back roads. FLORIDA ONE OWNER 2016 BENTLEY CONTINENTAL COUPE V8 WITH ONLY 5,553 MILES , YES 5,553 MILES , ABSOLUTELY IN LIKE BRAND NEW CONDITION IN A BEAUTIFUL COLOR COMBINATION , AGAIN LIKE NEW, CLEAN CARFAX ONE OWNER , PICTURES/ PRICING COMING SOON The Bentley Continental GT is a grand touring car manufactured and marketed by the British company Bentley Motors since 2003. The Continental GT is offered as a two-door coupé or convertible, with four seats. It was the first new Bentley released after the company's acquisition by Volkswagen AG in 1998, and the first Bentley to employ mass production manufacturing techniques. The GT V8 version of the Continental GT has a twin-turbo 4-litre (3,993 cc) V8 engine (developed jointly with Audi) that produces 500 hp (373 kW) and 487 lb·ft (660 N·m) of torque. The car is capable of reaching a top speed of 192 mph (309 km/h). It also features cylinder deactivation technology that can deactivate half of the cylinders when they're not needed to improve fuel economy by up to 8%. Other changes, including on-demand steering assistance, weight reduction, better engine heat management, overrun alternator charging and eco-tyres, improve overall fuel consumption by 40% from the W12's 17.1 mpg to the V8's 26.1 mpg . description:
2024 BMW M2
G87 Coupe

- Alpine White over Black Leather with M Accents
- S58 3.0L Twin Turbo Inline 6 Cylinder
- 6 Speed Manual Gearbox
- Dinan Experience Package, Installed Summer 2025 by German Auto Service LTD
- 537 Horsepower and 513 lb-ft of Torque
- Dinan Factory Matching 4-Year/50K Mile Warranty
- Dinan Experience Package Includes: Dinan+ PCU, Gloss Carbon Fiber Cold Air Intake, High Flow Exhaust and Mid Pipe, Gloss Carbon Fiber Strut Tower Brace, Dinan Pedal Covers ($12k)
- Apex VS-5RS Wheels ($4k)
- Michelin Pilot Sport Cup 2 Tires ($2,600)
- STEK Front End PPF ($2k)
- Oil Cooler and Vent Grille Set ($800)
- Noteworthy Factory Options: Shadowline and Lighting Packages, Carbon Fiber Roof and Trim, Heated Steering Wheel, Parking Assistant, Wireless Device Charging, Live Cockpit Pro with Heads Up Display
- Always Serviced at BMW Dealer or German Auto
- Both Keys, All Records, Books, and Window Sticker
- Non-Smoker, No Accidents, Clean Title - Needs Nothing
- All Factory Components Included with Sale
- 13k MilesThis 2024 BMW M2 G87 Coupe represents a tastefully modified example from our ownership, combining factory M performance with thoughtfully selected upgrades that elevate an already exceptional platform. Finished in timeless Alpine White over a Black leather interior with M accents, the M2's aggressive proportions, wide stance, and purposeful design are further enhanced by carbon fiber details and Shadowline trim, giving the car a clean yet unmistakably motorsport-inspired presence.At its core is BMW's renowned S58 3.0-liter twin-turbocharged inline-six, paired with a highly sought-after 6-speed manual gearbox. This setup delivers an engaging, driver-focused experience that modern performance cars rarely offer. Enhanced with the Dinan Experience Package installed in Summer 2025 by German Auto LTD, output is elevated to an impressive 537 horsepower and 513 lb-ft of torque (more HP than the new M2 CS), transforming the M2 into a truly formidable performer while retaining everyday drivability.The Dinan Experience Package is comprehensive and premium, featuring the Dinan+ PCU, gloss carbon fiber cold air intake, high-flow exhaust with mid pipe, carbon fiber strut tower brace, and Dinan pedal covers, over $12,000 in upgrades. Importantly, these enhancements are backed by a Dinan factory-matching 4-year/50,000-mile warranty, offering peace of mind alongside exhilarating performance. An upgraded oil cooler and vent grille set further support consistent performance under spirited driving conditions.Handling and grip are equally well addressed with lightweight Apex VS-5RS wheels wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport Cup 2 tires, a combination that dramatically sharpens turn-in and maximizes traction. A STEK front-end paint protection film has been professionally installed to preserve the Alpine White finish, ensuring the car remains as striking as it is capable.Inside, the cabin blends modern technology with motorsport flair. Noteworthy factory options include the carbon fiber roof and interior trim, Shadowline and Lighting Packages, heated steering wheel, parking assistant, wireless device charging, and Live Cockpit Professional with heads-up display. Every detail reinforces the M2's dual nature as both a serious performance machine and a refined daily driver.With just 13,000 miles, this M2 has been meticulously maintained, always serviced at a BMW dealer or respected German automotive specialist. description:
2024 BMW M4 Competition Coupe xDrive
Alpine White over Silverstone and Black Extended Merino Leather

The 2024 BMW M4 Competition Coupe is more than a vehicle, it is a precision instrument designed for those who view driving as an art form. This xDrive-equipped model balances the raw, visceral power of the M TwinPower Turbo engine with the sophisticated composure of intelligent all-wheel drive. Whether carving through a canyon or navigating a modern commute, the M4 Competition delivers an unmatched level of tactile feedback and confidence.

Performance and Handling
At the heart of this machine lies a 503-horsepower engine paired with a lightning-fast 8-speed M Steptronic transmission. The M xDrive system provides a rear-biased feel that maintains classic agility while offering maximum traction when you need it most. This specimen features M Compound Brakes with Red Calipers for exceptional stopping power and staggered 19-inch front and 20-inch rear Style 826M wheels.

Luxury and Technology
The interior is a focused cockpit, featuring the modern BMW Curved Display and an intuitive Head-Up Display that keeps vital information in your line of sight. The contrast of the Alpine White exterior against the Silverstone and Black Extended Merino Leather creates an atmosphere of contemporary elegance. Notable additions include the Executive Package, which adds a Heated Steering Wheel and Power Tailgate, and the Parking Assistance Package with Parking Assistant Plus. Front Ventilated Seats and Remote Engine Start ensure the cabin is perfectly tailored to your comfort before you even step inside.

Ownership and Confidence
This M4 Competition is a CARFAX One-Owner vehicle with a clean history and 35,029 miles. It has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to meet exacting standards. As a BMW Certified Pre-Owned (CPO) vehicle, it offers a level of security that standard pre-owned cars cannot match. You are supported by a BMW Certified Unlimited Mileage Warranty through November 3, 2028, featuring a zero-dollar deductible and 24/7 Roadside Assistance.

Experience the Ultimate Driving Machine
This M4 Competition represents a rare opportunity to own a late-model, high-performance coupe with the extensive protection of a BMW Certified warranty. To arrange a private viewing or a test drive, please contact our team at your convenience. We look forward to introducing you to your next BMW.
