description:
Discover the epitome of performance and style with this exceptional 2024 Chevrolet Corvette Stingray 2LT. This stunning sports car is more than just a head-turner – it's a masterpiece of engineering that will thrill you every time you get behind the wheel.

• Z51 Performance Package
• Tech Bronze Accent Package (LPO)
• GT2 Bucket Seats
• Carbon Flash Metallic-Painted Outside Mirrors and Spoiler
• Preferred Equipment Group 2LT
• 14-Speaker Bose Performance Series Sound System

The Corvette Stingray's 6.2L V8 engine and 8-speed dual-clutch transmission deliver exhilarating power and lightning-fast response, propelling you from 0 to 60 mph in a mere 3.6 seconds. The Z51 Performance Package enhances the driving experience with upgraded brakes, suspension, and an electronic limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional handling and control.

Step inside the cabin and you'll be surrounded by premium materials and thoughtful design. The GT2 bucket seats provide exceptional support and comfort, while the Bose Performance Series sound system immerses you in a rich, detailed audio experience. The Preferred Equipment Group 2LT adds a wealth of advanced technologies, including a head-up display, navigation, and a performance data and video recorder.

This Corvette Stingray also boasts a stunning exterior in White, complemented by the optional Tech Bronze Accent Package. The carbon fiber-reinforced plastic body panels not only look stunning but also contribute to the vehicle's lightweight and agile nature.

Prepare to be the envy of the road with this exceptional 2024 Chevrolet Corvette Stingray 2LT. Its combination of raw power, refined handling, and premium features make it a true driver's dream. Experience the thrill for yourself – schedule a test drive today and let this Corvette Stingray captivate your senses.

Don't forget this vehicle includes the Green Lifetime Powertrain Warranty and the Green's Goods Maintenance program. You Gotta Go Green.

This Porsche 718 Cayman S arrived from our service loaner fleet, and is an excellent sports car. White paint is complemented with sporty accents in the forms of 20-inch Carrera S Wheels in High Gloss Black, and sport tailpipes in Black. The equally sporty interior features gorgeous Bordeaux Red leather, with a matching Sport Chrono Stopwatch Dial. The car comes equipped with a fire extinguisher, to provide extra safety, and a true racecar feel! The Sport Chrono Package increases the performance of this already zippy coupe, and a 6-speed manual transmission mated to its 4-cylinder Boxer motor makes for an exhilarating driving experience!


Porsche Approved Certified Pre-Owned (CPO):

- Zero warranty deductible
- 111 point inspection
- Transferable warranty (between private parties)
- Roadside assistance
- Factory coverage to 04/29/2031 with no mileage limitation!

description:
SweetCars is proud to present this 2024 Porsche Cayman Style Edition!
This stunning Cayman is finished in Gentian Blue Metallic over a Black/Chalk interior, further complemented by white Style Edition graphics and optional Satin Aurum finished wheels. Factory options on this 718 include:
a 6-speed manual transmission, Porsche Torque Vectoring, Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), Satiun Aurim finished wheels, rear window wiper, clear taillights, Bose Surround Sound System, GT Sport Steering wheel and Chalk seat belts.
This Porsche comes with two master keys and factory owners manuals. A CarFax report is viewable for free via our website. You can also drive with peace of mind as the car comes with the remainder of its original manufacturers basic and drivetrain warranty!
When purchasing this Cayman Style Edition, you will experience the SweetCars Difference. What does the SweetCars Difference mean? We search the country for the very best inventory and hand-select each vehicle we offer for sale. Each vehicle receives a thorough inspection from our experienced technicians and a meticulous detail from our award-winning detailing team. During our listing process, we ensure every vehicle is offered at the highest level possible. All fluid services are confirmed to be up-to-date, wear items are checked to be within proper ranges and all functions of the vehicle are tested.
Not able to come see this beauty in-person? Not a problem! At SweetCars, weve sold vehicles all over the world and our expert Sales Consultants specialize in assisting our customers with making the transaction as easy as possible. We are happy to assist with providing additional pictures, videos, vehicle information, coordination of PPIs, open or enclosed shipping and more!
Be sure to ask your Sales Consultant about our highline protection packages including Ceramic Pro ceramic coatings, SunTek Paint Protection Film and window tint!
Contact a SweetCars representative now to park this Porsche 718 Style Edition in your garage today!

description: 2024 Lotus Emira V6 First Edition The Stradman's Emira, 6-Speed Manual, Seneca Blue THIS... is a 2024 Lotus Emira First Edition, finished in Seneca Blue with an Ice Grey interior. This Emira is equipped with a 6-speed manual transmission. The attached Carfax history report lists no accidents or mileage discrepancies in this Emira's brief past. According to the window sticker provided in the gallery, factory equipment includes the Lotus Driver, Convenience, and Lower Black packs, 20-inch forged wheels, yellow brake calipers, sport suspension, heated and power-adjustable front seats, leather upholstery, a KEF Uni-Q audio system, and wireless Android Auto and Apple CarPlay compatibility. Modifications reported by the seller are limited to a GRP titanium exhaust system and tinted windows. Lotus introduced the Emira in 2021 as the replacement for the outgoing Evora. The Emira represents a leap forward in terms of technology, notably, this is Lotus' first vehicle to include optional active safety features such as adaptive cruise control, automated emergency braking, and lane departure warning. The Toyota-sourced supercharged V6 was carried over from the Evora, and is still offered with a 6-speed manual transmission. Power comes from a Toyota-derived 3.5-liter supercharged V6, rated at 400 horsepower and 310 lb-ft of torque. Output is sent to the rear wheels via a 6-speed manual transmission. Lotus Driver Pack (Track Mode with HMI/TFT display, limited-slip differential, valved exhaust) Convenience Pack (front parking sensors, rear-view camera, rain-sensing windshield wipers, auto-dimming rear and side-view mirrors, cargo net) Lower Black Pack 20-inch diamond cut forged wheels Yellow brake calipers Sport suspension LED headlights and taillights Leather upholstery Heated and power-adjustable seats 12.3-inch TFT instrument display Dual-zone automatic climate control KEF Uni-Q 560-watt audio system 10.25-inch HMI touchscreen Wireless Android Auto and Apple CarPlay compatibility

description: The 2022 Dodge Challenger SRT Super Stock is a bold expression of American muscle, merging raw power with modern sophistication. Under the hood, it boasts a supercharged 6.2-liter HEMI V8 engine delivering an astonishing 807 horsepower, making it one of the most powerful production cars on the market. Built for both the drag strip and street, the Super Stock comes equipped with performance-tuned suspension, wide drag radial tires, and high-performance Brembo brakes. It not only delivers heart-pounding acceleration but also commands presence with an aggressive stance and signature Xenon headlights that provide superior nighttime visibility and a striking visual appeal.----Inside the cabin, the Challenger SRT Super Stock offers a blend of high-performance design and modern technology. Premium leather seats provide both comfort and support, perfect for long drives or spirited sprints. The cutting-edge infotainment system includes Apple CarPlay and Android Auto for seamless smartphone connectivity, putting navigation, calls, and music at your fingertips. Enhancing the in-car experience further, the premium audio system delivers crystal-clear sound that matches the car's commanding performance. A built-in Wi-Fi hotspot ensures you stay connected on the road, whether streaming media or staying productive while traveling. Altogether, the 2022 Dodge Challenger SRT Super Stock offers the perfect mix of brute strength and refined tech, making it an irresistible choice for enthusiasts who demand power without sacrificing comfort or connectivity.

708 HP SUPERCHARGED V8 -- 7-SPEED AUTOMATIC -- ADAPTIVE SUSPENSION -- 20" HIGH GLOSS ALUMINUM WHEELS -- LEATHER-TRIMMED SPORT SEATS -- SYNC 3 WITH SIRIUSXM -- DUAL-ZONE CLIMATE CONTROL -- BRAKE ASSIST -- REAR CAMERA

Feel the thunder of American muscle with the 2022 Ford Mustang Shelby GT500, a masterpiece of performance and design. This beast, cloaked in stunning Gray Metallic paint, roars to life with its 5.2L supercharged V8 engine, delivering a pulse-quickening 708 horsepower. Paired with a seamless 7-speed automatic transmission, the thrill of rear-wheel drive comes alive with every acceleration, making this not just a car, but an adrenaline-fueled experience.

Slide into the Ebony leather-trimmed seats with gray accents, and youll discover a world of high-intensity comfort. The climate-controlled front seats ensure you stay cozy or cool, no matter the weather. Let the automatic dual-zone air conditioning cater to you and your passenger's comfort needs. Power adjustments for both driver and passenger seats allow you to find your perfect driving position with ease, making every journey as comfortable as it is exhilarating.

With SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System at your fingertips, connected driving has never been this intuitive. Access SiriusXM radio through a nine-speaker sound system that transforms any playlist into a live concert experience. Steering wheel-mounted controls and voice activation enable you to stay engaged with the road without distraction. Adding to the practicality is the rear window defroster and the convenience of power windows and mirrors, ensuring clear vision and top functionality.

Safety is paramount in the Shelby GT500, and it doesnt disappoint. Equipped with ABS brakes, dual front and side impact airbags, brake assist, and an emergency communication system, peace of mind comes as standard. The built-in rearview camera with parking assistance gives you the confidence needed for city driving or precision parking. Electronic Stability Control and traction control ensure the vehicles power is harnessed with precision.

Aggressively styled with a painted black roof and bold 20" flow-formed high gloss black aluminum wheels, this Mustang stands out from every angle. The adaptive suspension keeps you comfortable on different terrains, while speed-sensing steering helps you maintain control. It's more than just a ride its a statement.

Experience legendary performance and innovative tech at Guntersville Chevrolet. We deliver excellence with transparent pricing and a hassle-free experience. Dont miss your chance to unleash the icon within. Visit us today and drive the 2022 Ford Mustang Shelby GT500. Lets make your dream driveway a reality!

description: The 2018 Dodge Challenger SRT Demon is a legendary American muscle car engineered for top-tier performance and exclusivity. Under the hood lies a supercharged 6.2-liter HEMI V8 engine delivering up to 840 horsepower, making it the most powerful factory-produced V8 car ever built. This particular model comes equipped with the Quick Order Package 26M, emphasizing both performance and comfort. Inside, the Demon boasts the Laguna Leather/Alcantara Performance Seat package with the exclusive Demon logo, enhancing the cabin's race-inspired design while offering luxury materials. Leather seats and the Rear Seat Option with leather trim and distinctive red seat belts add style and functionality, making this Demon more accommodating for everyday use without sacrificing its aggressive edge.----The Demon also includes an array of premium features, including a Power Sunroof, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and an advanced Navigation system for connectivity and convenience on the road. The Premium Audio system ensures superior sound quality, while the Comfort Audio Group – Leather Seats package elevates the driving experience further. A Trunk Carpet Kit enhances the appearance and practicality of the cargo space, and the Demon Vehicle Storage Package allows for proper storage options when the car is not tearing up the track. This rare and well-optioned SRT Demon perfectly blends raw power with modern luxury, offering a unique opportunity for collectors and driving enthusiasts alike to own a piece of muscle car history.

THRILLING 6.2L V8 -- Z51 PERFORMANCE PKG -- CUSTOM LEATHER -- HEAD-UP DISPLAY -- DUAL ROOF PACKAGE -- BOSE AUDIO -- HEATED/COOLED SEATS -- APPLE CARPLAY/ANDROID AUTO -- MAGNETIC RIDE CONTROL

Welcome to the exhilarating world of sports car excellence with this 2020 Chevrolet Corvette Stingray 3LT, finished in a striking Sebring Orange Tintcoat. It's a true masterpiece of motoring innovation, embodying the Corvette's legendary spirit with every rev of its 6.2L V8 engine. This sleek 2D coupe is all about precision and power, offering rear-wheel drive greatness and an 8-speed dual-clutch transmission that shifts seamlessly through the gears.

Inside, you'll find an environment crafted for the ultimate driving experience featuring Chevrolet's Custom Leather-Wrapped Interior Package. The Jet Black interior perfectly complements the bold exterior, adding an elegant touch. Achieve optimal comfort with GT2 bucket seats that are both heated and cooled, while memory settings for the driver and passenger ensure your preferences are never lost. Dual-zone automatic climate control keeps everyone at their preferred temperature, making long drives effortlessly enjoyable.

Technology elevates command on the road with the Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Premium System, complete with advanced navigation and wireless charging for your devices. The Bose Performance Series Sound System with 14 speakers fills the cabin with crystal-clear audio, from your favorite driving playlist to the crisp directions delivered via Apple CarPlay or Android Auto. A head-up display projects essential information right onto the windshield, meaning your eyes are always where they should beon the road ahead.

Safety is just as paramount as performance in the Corvette Stingray. With features such as side blind zone alert, rear cross-traffic alert, and an HD camera system, you're surrounded by an intelligent safety suite. The Z51 Performance Brakes and suspension ensure stopping power and handling meet the highest expectations, delivering confidence at every turn. Whether you're navigating city streets or the open highway, this Corvette offers peace of mind with OnStar and Chevrolet's connected services.

Imagine weekends spent carving through winding roads with the Z51 Performance Package making each corner a thrill. The body-color dual roof package lets you cruise with style, rain or shine, while the performance exhaust with stainless-steel tips not only sounds breathtaking but looks the part. This Corvette isn't just a vehicleit's an invitation to indulge in the art of driving, offering the perfect lifestyle fit for those who live for the thrill of the road.

At Newton Ford South, we're committed to making your car buying journey as enjoyable as a ride in this Corvette. Experience genuine, friendly service backed by our stellar reputation and hassle-free financing options. Don't let this opportunity speed byvisit us today to see, hear, and feel the excitement this Corvette brings to life.

description:
The 2020 Chevrolet Camaro RWD Coupe Preferred Equipment Group ZL1 is a powerful sports car that perfectly balances performance, technology, and comfort. With its robust 6.2L V-8 engine producing a staggering 650 horsepower and paired with a Tremec 6-speed manual transmission, the Camaro ZL1 is engineered for speed enthusiasts who crave exhilarating driving experiences.

This model comes equipped with state-of-the-art technology that enhances your driving experience. One of the key features is the smart device mirroring capability, which allows you to seamlessly connect your smartphone to the vehicle’s infotainment system. This feature ensures that you can access your favorite apps and music without taking your eyes off the road, promoting both safety and convenience.

Additionally, the Camaro ZL1 includes a built-in mobile hotspot, enabling you to stay connected to the internet wherever your adventures may take you. This feature helps you save on mobile data while providing you access to online resources during your drive, whether you’re navigating through city traffic or cruising on the highway.

Safety is paramount in the Camaro ZL1, featuring a rear camera that enhances visibility, allowing you to detect obstacles while reversing. The head-up display is another innovative feature, projecting vital driving information such as speed and RPM directly onto the windshield, ensuring you remain focused on the road ahead.

For long journeys, the Camaro ZL1 offers cruise control with steering wheel-mounted controls, making it easy to maintain a steady speed without continuous pedal pressure. This not only reduces driver fatigue but also optimizes fuel efficiency, making it a superb choice for road trips. The comfort factor is elevated with ventilated front seats, providing a refreshing breeze on hot days, alongside heated front seats and a heated steering wheel for those cold mornings.

Navigating your way is a breeze with the voice-activated integrated navigation system, allowing you to simply speak your destination and receive clear directions, eliminating the frustration of traditional maps.

In conclusion, the 2020 Chevrolet Camaro RWD Coupe Preferred Equipment Group ZL1 stands out as a remarkable blend of power, advanced safety features, and cutting-edge technology. Perfect for both daily commutes and weekend adventures, this vehicle promises to deliver an unforgettable driving experience that combines thrill and practicality. Dont miss out on the chance to elevate your journey with the Camaro ZL1!

description:
2020 CHEVROLET CORVETTE STINGRAY 3LT

Z51 PERFORMANCE PACKAGE, BOSE PERFORMANCE AUDIO SYSTEM, FRONT LIFT, AND MORE!

OVERVIEW
Meet the most track-focused Corvette ever built. This 2020 Chevrolet Corvette Stingray 3LT is an embodiment of pure American muscle and exotic-car performance designed to take on the head honchos from overseas. Power comes from a mid-mounted 6.2L naturally aspirated LT2 V8 making 495 hp and 465 lb-ft of torque directed through an 8-speed dual clutch transmission. The result comes in the form of a 0-60 mph time of just 2.9 seconds. Visually, the Stingray commands attention with its sharp aerodynamic lines, wide stance, and aggressive air intakes. This Torch Red example is spec'd with the Z51 Performance Package and Magnetic Ride Control for increased performance and power. With its removable roof panel, it transforms into an open-air driving experience in seconds. The 3LT package elevates the Stingray's cabin into a luxury experience, featuring Adrenaline Red leather seating surfaces, heated/ventilated GT2 bucket seats, and contrast stitching throughout. A Bose Performance audio system, head-up display, and wireless Apple CarPlay/Android Auto keep the driver seamlessly connected. The Chevrolet Corvette Stingray 3LT isn't just a leap forward for American sports cars––it's a world-class supercar engineered to challenge Europe's best, both on the street and the circuit.

description: 2020 BMW M8 Competition CoupeOne Owner!Clean Carfax!M Drivers Package, Driving Assistance Professional Package, Bowers & Wilkins Diamond Surround Sound System 4.4L Twin-Turbo V8 8-Speed Automatic AWD Alpine White Exterior Sakhir Orange/Black Interior Full Merino Leather Interior Driving Assistance Professional Package Active Cruise Control with Stop and Go Active Lane Keeping Assist Traffic Jam Assist Active Driving Assistant Pro Active Park Distance Control Drive Recorder Surround View 3D View Rear View Camera Bowers & Wilkins Diamond Surround Sound System M Drivers PackageThe current-generation BMW M8 is the M-division's take on BMW's 8-Series grand tourer. Originally debuting for the 2019 model year, the 8-Series comes as a coupe and convertible, plus a four-door Gran Coupe. As you'd expect, the M8 comes with plenty of power, performance and character. This particular 2020 BMW M8 Competition is no different,If you want something close to a supercar but with signature BMW luxury, this car is the ticket.This 2020 BMW M8 Competition is cloaked in Alpine White, a stunning shade that brings out its beautiful design. The car rides on an intricate set of 20-inch alloy wheels in gunmetal gray, behind which lurk blue M brake calipers. The tires on this car are high-performance Michelin Pilot Sport units. At the front, you've got glaring LED headlamps, while the rear LED taillamps leave their mark as you drive by. The quad exhaust tips are another M-division hallmark, as they allow the turbocharged V8 to emit a distinctive roar. Inside, there's a lovely Sakhir Orange and Black four-seat cabin waiting to be enjoyed. The front seats are heated and power-adjustable units, while the rear seats offer surprising amounts of head and legroom for what is, in effect, a two-door coupe. There's a Bowers & Wilkins upgraded sound system, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto for infotainment needs. It's all controlled via BMW's slick iDrive interface, which can be accessed via a rotary controller in the center console, as well as the touchscreen on the dash. There's dual-zone climate control to keep everyone comfortable and the obligatory features of power windows, mirrors, and door locks. The driver gets a multifunction steering wheel and gazes at a customizable digital instrument cluster. Gear shift paddles are present, too, as well as two smaller red 'M' paddles for accessing special modes. Look closer, and you'll even spot child seat anchors in the rear seats of this 2020 BMW M8 Competition. That, coupled with its amazingly accommodating trunk, makes it a practical car. As practical as it may be, this 2020 BMW M8 Competition has a superb 4.4L twin-turbocharged V8 under the hood, just waiting to be woken up. When you do, it unleashes 617hp and 553lb-ft to all four wheels via an 8-speed ZF automatic transmission and BMW's xDrive all-wheel-drive system. You can easily achieve 0-60 in under 3.5 seconds. When it's time to stop, large ventilated brakes can reign the car in with confidence every time.

description:
If you have been searching for the ultimate modern drivers car, this 2025 BMW M2 is exactly the kind of spec enthusiasts wait for.

Finished in timeless Alpine White, this M2 is powered by BMWs turbocharged inline-six and paired with the most desirable option of all: a 6-speed manual transmission. In a world moving away from true driver engagement, the manual M2 stands out as one of the most exciting performance cars you can still buy.

This is a CARFAX One-Owner vehicle with a Clean CARFAX, representing the type of well-kept example serious buyers want.

What truly sets this M2 apart is the rare and highly sought-after M Carbon Bucket Seats. These are not just an interior option, they are a statement. Built for maximum support and weight reduction, the carbon buckets completely transform the driving experience and give the cabin a true motorsport feel. Cars equipped with these seats are significantly harder to find and are always at the top of the list for serious M enthusiasts.

Adding to the performance-focused spec is the M Carbon Roof, lowering the center of gravity while giving the car an aggressive, high-end look that will age beautifully over time.

This M2 has also been exceptionally cared for cosmetically. The vehicle was fully cut and buffed, and two layers of professional ceramic coating were applied less than 4,000 miles ago, giving the paint an incredible finish and added long-term protection.

Other standout features include:

6-Speed Manual Transmission
Rear-Wheel Drive Performance
M Carbon Bucket Seats
M Carbon Roof
harman/kardon Premium Surround Sound
Merino Leather Upholstery
Navigation with Widescreen Display
Adaptive Suspension
Heated Front Seats
Staggered 19-inch front and 20-inch rear wheels

The reality is simple: manual M cars with carbon buckets do not last long. This is one of the most desirable configurations available, and it represents a rare opportunity to own a properly specd M2 that will only become more sought after over time.

Key Highlights
2025 BMW M2
Alpine White
6-Speed Manual
CARFAX One-Owner Clean CARFAX
M Carbon Bucket Seats
M Carbon Roof
Two-Layer Ceramic Coating Applied Under 4,000 Miles Ago
harman/kardon Audio
Merino Leather Interior
Adaptive Suspension
Low Availability Enthusiast Spec

If you have been waiting for the right M2, this is the one you want to see in person.

Visit WinslowBMW.com or call 719-473-1373 today to schedule your test drive. Pricing includes a $299 delivery and handling fee.

Inside, the cabin features a black leather interior accented by eye-catching blue seatbelts, reinforcing the Dark Horses motorsport-inspired character. Designed with the driver in mind, the interior combines modern technology, supportive seating, and premium materials to create an engaging and immersive driving environment. Blending cutting-edge performance capability with unmistakable Mustang heritage, this 2025 Ford Mustang Dark Horse stands out as an exceptional choice for enthusiasts seeking a powerful and distinctive American performance coupe.

Boasting a powerful 5.0L V8 DOHC 32V engine, the Mustang Dark Horse is equipped with a 10-Speed Automatic transmission and Rear-Wheel Drive, providing an unparalleled driving dynamic. With 15 MPG in the city and 23 MPG on the highway, this vehicle offers a thrilling blend of performance and efficiency.

Beneath the sculpted hood, the 5.0L V8 engine roars to life, delivering an exhilarating driving experience that will leave you breathless. The Mustang Dark Horse's handling is equally impressive, thanks to its Adaptive Suspension and Four Wheel Independent Suspension, which provide a perfect balance of responsiveness and comfort.

Safety is also a top priority in the Mustang Dark Horse, with features like Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, and Electronic Stability Control ensuring your peace of mind on the road.

Whether you're looking to conquer the open road or turn heads on the streets, the 2025 Ford Mustang Dark Horse is the ultimate performance machine. Experience the power, the style, and the uncompromising driving dynamics that make this vehicle a true legend in the world of sports cars.

Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Mustang Dark Horse is the perfect choice for the discerning driver. We're confident that once you take it for a test drive, you'll be hooked on the thrill of owning this exceptional vehicle.

description:
Check out this 2025 Ford Mustang Dark Horse finished in Molten Magenta Metallic Tri-coat with a Black w/Blue Accents interior. This vehicle is equipped with the following features and options: Equipment Group 600A High Package
  • Cloth/vinyl Heated Bucket Seats
  • TREMEC 6-Speed Manual Transmission
  • MOD 5.0L-4V DOHC EFI NA Engine
  • AM/FM Stereo
Convenience
  • GPS linked cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until GPS linked cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed and the system uses GPS navigation data to maintain that speed without driver intervention - including slowing down for curves and anticipating hills. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, GPS linked cruise control.
  • Distance pacing cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. Distance pacing cruise control, your ultimate co-pilot.
Safety and Security
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Rear collision mitigation - It has your back. Rear collision mitigation uses sensors to monitor the area behind you. If it senses an impending crash, it activates certain features to help prevent a collision or reduce the severity of it. Put your worries behind you with rear collision mitigation.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
  • Predictive brake assist - Be prepared for your big brake. Predictive brake assist monitors the available distance in front of you compared to your vehicles speed. If your speed exceeds the required distance to stop short of a collision, it readies your brakes to apply maximum stopping force when you use them. Predictive brake assist helps see to it that you stop.
Technology and Telematics
  • SYNC 4 AppLink/Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

With an original MSRP of $73,425, this 2025 BMW M2 delivers an uncompromising blend of motorsport performance, aggressive styling, and modern technology in a compact high-performance coupe. Designed for driving enthusiasts, the M2 pairs BMW M engineering with premium appointments and a focused, driver-centric layout.

This example is equipped with a carbon fiber roof, a $2,600 factory option that reduces weight and lowers the center of gravity while adding a distinctive performance look. Inside, the cabin features black Vernasca leather upholstery with bold red highlights, complemented by carbon fiber interior trim for a true M-inspired atmosphere. The M Alcantara steering wheel enhances grip and driver connection, while the Lighting Package and M Shadowline lights add both visual appeal and functionality.

Technology highlights include Live Cockpit Pro with a head-up display that projects key driving information directly into the drivers line of sight, a Harman Kardon premium sound system for immersive audio, and a wireless device charging pad for added convenience. Apple CarPlay integration allows seamless smartphone connectivity, and the rearview camera assists with parking and low-speed maneuvering. Combining raw performance, advanced technology, and premium materials, this 2025 BMW M2 stands out as a thrilling and well-equipped modern M car.

Compact, aggressive, and purpose-built, the M2 delivers an exhilarating experience that puts the driver at the center of every mile.A performance-tuned engine delivers thrilling acceleration and a spine-tingling soundtrack, while BMW M engineering provides razor-sharp handling and exceptional balance. With a wide stance, rear-wheel-drive dynamics, and track-inspired tuning, the M2 Coupe feels equally at home carving through back roads or commanding attention on city streets. Every input feels connected, responsive, and intensely engaging.Inside, the cockpit is designed with a driver-first mindset, blending motorsport influence with premium BMW craftsmanship. Supportive sport seating, high-quality materials, and intuitive controls create an immersive environment that enhances focus and comfort. Advanced digital displays and performance-focused technology keep vital information easily accessible, allowing you to stay connected to both the road and the machine.Engineered for those who crave authenticity and adrenaline, the 2025 BMW M2 Coupe represents the purest expression of BMW M performance. From its aggressive presence to its thrilling driving dynamics, this coupe delivers an uncompromising blend of power, precision, and passion.Visit BMW of West Houston at 20822 Katy Fwy Katy, TX 77449 today!

description:
Discover the Thrill of the 2025 BMW M2 Base

Unlock the exhilaration of pure driving dynamics with the 2025 BMW M2 Base. This exceptional sports coupe is a rare find, boasting a captivating blend of power, precision, and uncompromising style. Crafted to ignite your passion for the road, the M2 Base delivers an unparalleled driving experience that will leave you craving more.

• RARE - Manual Transmission
• One Owner - Clean Car Fax
• APPLE CarPlay
• Navigation/GPS
• Front & Rear Parking Sensors
• Rear Cross Traffic Alert
• Forward Collision Warning
• Power Moonroof/Sunroof
• Heated - Leather Seats
• 161 - Multi Point Service Inspection
• Fully Serviced & White Gloved Detailed
• M Carbon Roof
• Frozen Pure Grey Metallic
• Carbon Fiber Trim
• Lighting Package (Adaptive Full LED Lights, Automatic High Beams)
• M Alcantara Steering Wheel

Beneath the stunning Frozen Pure Grey Metallic exterior lies the heart of a true performance machine. Powered by a 3.0L inline-6 engine and paired with a thrilling 6-speed manual transmission, the M2 Base delivers an exhilarating driving experience that will leave you captivated. The rear-wheel-drive layout and M-tuned suspension ensure precise handling and exceptional agility, allowing you to carve through corners with confidence.

The M2 Base is more than just a sports car, it's a statement of your passion for the driving experience. The exclusive M Carbon Roof and Carbon Fiber Trim accentuate the vehicle's athletic silhouette, while the Lighting Package with Adaptive Full LED Lights and Automatic High Beams provide enhanced visibility and style.

Step inside the cabin, and you'll be enveloped in a world of premium features that cater to your every need. The Heated Leather Seats, M Alcantara Steering Wheel, and Widescreen Display create an environment that seamlessly blends comfort and technology. Enjoy the rich, immersive sound of the harman/kardon Surround Sound System as you navigate the roads with the intuitive guidance of the Navigation System.

description:
The 2025 Chevrolet Corvette Stingray 1LT is a true masterpiece of automotive engineering, designed to thrill and captivate the senses. With its stunning Red exterior and a powerful 6.2L V8 engine, this Corvette is ready to deliver an unparalleled driving experience.

Featuring a curated selection of premium upgrades, this Corvette Stingray 1LT stands out from the crowd:

• Wheels: 19" x 8.5" Front and 20" x 11" Rear 5-Open-Spoke Carbon Flash-Painted Aluminum with Machined Edge
• Calipers: Bright Red-Painted
• Carbon Flash Metallic-Painted Outside Mirrors and Spoiler

Beyond the eye-catching aesthetics, this Corvette Stingray 1LT is packed with a wealth of advanced technology and comfort features, including a Navigation System, Preferred Equipment Group 1LT, and a Premium audio system with 10 speakers.

Slip behind the wheel and experience the thrill of the 8-Speed Dual Clutch transmission, which delivers lightning-fast gear changes and seamless power delivery. With an EPA-estimated 16 city/24 highway MPG, this Corvette Stingray 1LT offers the perfect balance of performance and efficiency.

The cabin of this Corvette Stingray 1LT is a testament to Chevrolet's commitment to craftsmanship and attention to detail. Mulan Leather Seating Surfaces with Perforated Inserts provide exceptional comfort and support, while the 8-Way Power Driver and Passenger Seats ensure a personalized fit.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2025 Chevrolet Corvette Stingray 1LT. With its stunning design, exhilarating performance, and premium features, this Corvette is poised to exceed your expectations and leave a lasting impression. We invite you to schedule a test drive and discover the true essence of American sports car excellence.

description:
Experience the perfect blend of luxury, performance, and style with this stunning 2018 Lexus LC 500, now available at Motorcars Louisiana. This exceptional vehicle is a testament to Lexus's commitment to crafting high-performance luxury automobiles that captivate the senses and deliver an exhilarating driving experience. With its striking design, powerful engine, and luxurious interior, the LC 500 is a true masterpiece on wheels.

The 2018 Lexus LC 500 boasts an eye-catching Ultra White exterior that exudes sophistication and elegance. Its sleek, aerodynamic lines and bold front grille make a powerful statement on the road, while the sculpted bodywork and distinctive LED headlights enhance its modern aesthetic. The LC 500's design is not only visually stunning but also engineered for optimal performance, ensuring that it turns heads wherever it goes.

Step inside the LC 500, and you'll be greeted by a luxurious Rioja Red interior that perfectly complements its striking exterior. The cabin is a sanctuary of comfort and refinement, featuring high-quality materials and meticulous craftsmanship. The seats are upholstered in premium leather, providing exceptional support and comfort for both driver and passengers. The interior is thoughtfully designed with intuitive controls and advanced technology, ensuring a seamless and enjoyable driving experience.

Under the hood, the 2018 Lexus LC 500 is powered by a formidable 5.0L V8 engine that delivers an impressive 471 horsepower and 398 lb-ft of torque. This powerhouse engine is paired with a smooth and responsive 10-speed automatic transmission, providing exhilarating acceleration and precise handling. The rear-wheel-drive (RWD) drivetrain enhances the vehicle's dynamic performance, making every drive a thrilling adventure. With an EPA-estimated 16 MPG in the city and 26 MPG on the highway, the LC 500 offers a perfect balance of power and efficiency.

This LC 500 is equipped with a host of advanced features designed to enhance your driving experience. Key features include:

- Premium sound system for an immersive audio experience
- Advanced navigation system with real-time traffic updates

description:
This 2018 Porsche Cayman S is a one owner, no accident Carfax car with just 30,000 miles, finished in the highly desirable Chalk exterior over a Black and Chalk leather interior. This color combination is especially sought after and gives the car a clean, modern, and very upscale look that stands out without being loud. The low mileage and clean ownership history make this an excellent example for anyone looking for a well kept and properly optioned Cayman S.

Power comes from the turbocharged flat four engine paired with the PDK transmission, delivering quick shifts and strong performance while still being easy to live with day to day. This car is equipped with the Sport Chrono Package, which sharpens throttle response and driving dynamics, along with Porsche Entry and Drive for added convenience. The driving experience is pure Porsche, with excellent balance, steering feel, and confidence whether on back roads or the highway.

Notable options include 20 inch Carrera Sport wheels painted in high gloss black, a heated multifunction steering wheel, 14 way power sport seats with memory, Bose surround sound system, Porsche Connect, and seat heating. The Black and Chalk leather interior adds a premium feel that complements the exterior perfectly. With its desirable spec, low mileage, and clean history, this Cayman S represents a fantastic opportunity to own a modern Porsche that blends performance, refinement, and everyday usability.

description: Step into the world of unparalleled luxury and performance with this 2012 Bentley Continental GT, now available at Private Collection Motors. This remarkable grand tourer is a testament to Bentley's commitment to craftsmanship, elegance, and power, offering an unforgettable driving experience that is both thrilling and refined. Draped in a white paint finish, this Continental GT exudes a timeless sophistication that is sure to turn heads wherever you go. The sleek, aerodynamic lines of the body are accentuated by Bentley's signature matrix grille and striking bi-xenon headlights, which provide a commanding presence on the road. The sculpted rear haunches and distinctive LED tail lamps further enhance its dynamic stance, making it a true icon of automotive design. Step inside, and you'll be enveloped in an opulent interior that showcases Bentley's dedication to luxury and comfort. The rich brown leather upholstery is meticulously hand-stitched, offering a warm and inviting atmosphere. The cabin is adorned with exquisite wood veneers and polished chrome accents, creating a harmonious blend of traditional craftsmanship and modern technology. The front seats are not only heated and ventilated but also feature a massage function, ensuring that every journey is as comfortable as it is exhilarating. Under the hood lies the heart of this magnificent machinea 6.0L Flex Fuel Twin Turbo W12 engine that delivers an astonishing 567 horsepower and 516 lb-ft of torque. This powerhouse propels the Continental GT from 0 to 60 mph in just 4.4 seconds, providing an exhilarating driving experience that is both smooth and responsive. The advanced all-wheel-drive system ensures optimal traction and stability, allowing you to conquer any road with confidence. This 2012 Bentley Continental GT is more than just a car, it is a statement of style, power, and sophistication. Whether you're cruising down the highway or navigating city streets, this grand tourer offers an unparalleled driving experience that is sure to leave a lasting impression. Powered by the efficient and responsive SKYACTIV® 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, mated to a 6-Speed Automatic transmission and All-Wheel Drive, this CX-50 delivers an exceptional balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 24 city/30 highway MPG.

Step inside and discover a cabin that seamlessly blends style and functionality. Enjoy the comfort of Half Leatherette Seat Trim, the convenience of Steering Wheel-Mounted Audio Controls, and the connectivity of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. The Bose® 8-Speaker Audio System provides a premium listening experience, while the Rearview Camera and Blind Spot Monitoring with Rear Cross-Traffic Alert enhance your awareness on the road.

Safety is a top priority, and this CX-50 delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. Features like Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane Departure Warning, and Adaptive Cruise Control work together to help keep you and your loved ones protected.

Whether you're embarking on a weekend adventure or navigating the daily commute, the 2024 Mazda CX-50 2.5 S Select Package is the perfect companion. With its striking design, impressive capabilities, and thoughtful amenities, this SUV is poised to exceed your expectations and elevate your driving experience.

We invite you to visit our showroom and experience the exceptional 2024 Mazda CX-50 2.5 S Select Package for yourself. Let us demonstrate how this remarkable SUV can enhance your lifestyle and become the perfect addition to your family. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and unlock the full potential of the CX-50.

Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2020 Chevrolet Corvette Stingray 2LT. This sports car is a true masterpiece, combining exceptional performance, sophisticated style, and an array of premium features that will captivate your senses.

Indulge in the thrill of the open road with this Corvette's impressive 6.2L V8 engine, delivering a heart-pounding 8-speed dual-clutch transmission and rear-wheel drive. Elevate your commute with a remarkable fuel efficiency of 15 city/27 highway MPG. Seamlessly navigate your journeys with the convenience of a backup camera, Bluetooth connectivity, and leather-appointed seating.

- Backup Camera
- Bluetooth
- Leather Seats
- Leather Wrap Steering Wheel
- Front Lift Adjustable Height with Memory
- Performance Exhaust with Stainless-Steel Tips

This Corvette Stingray 2LT is meticulously equipped to elevate your driving experience. Enjoy the added confidence of the Front Lift Adjustable Height with Memory feature, allowing you to easily navigate uneven surfaces. The Performance Exhaust with Stainless-Steel Tips enhances the already thrilling exhaust note, providing an aural delight with every drive.

Step inside and be captivated by the premium Mulan Leather Seating Surfaces with Perforated Inserts, offering unparalleled comfort and style. The Bose Performance Series Sound System with 14 Speakers delivers an immersive audio experience, while the Heads-Up Display keeps your vital information in your line of sight.

This Corvette Stingray 2LT is a true testament to Chevrolet's commitment to excellence. With its striking Blue exterior, this sports car commands attention wherever it goes. Prepare to be the center of admiration as you effortlessly navigate the roads in this stunning and capable machine.

Experience the pinnacle of performance, luxury, and technology with this 2020 Chevrolet Corvette Stingray 2LT. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional vehicle can elevate your driving experience to new heights. We're confident you'll be captivated by its unparalleled blend of style, power, and sophistication.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with the 2026 BMW 2 Series 230i xDrive. This exceptional vehicle boasts a captivating blend of performance, technology, and style, making it the perfect companion for the discerning driver.

Equipped with a powerful 2.0L I4 16V TwinPower Turbo engine and an 8-Speed Automatic Sport transmission, the 2 Series delivers an exhilarating driving experience, with an impressive EPA-estimated 25 MPG in the city and 33 MPG on the highway. Paired with the xDrive all-wheel-drive system, this BMW offers exceptional handling and control, ensuring you can tackle any road with confidence.

• Premium Package: Includes Remote Engine Start, Adaptive Full LED Lights, Live Cockpit Pro with Head-Up Display, Heated Steering Wheel, Moonroof, Automatic High Beams, and Universal Garage-Door Opener
• 19" x 8.0" Individual Y-Spoke Bicolor Wheels
• Distance Control (ACC)

The 2 Series is brimming with cutting-edge technology and premium features, elevating your driving experience to new heights. Enjoy the convenience of Remote Engine Start, the clarity of Adaptive Full LED Lights, and the seamless integration of the Live Cockpit Pro with Head-Up Display. Stay connected with the Navigation System, 10-speaker Hi-Fi Sound System, and Apple CarPlay/Android Auto compatibility. The Heated Steering Wheel and Heated Front Seats provide a cozy and comfortable ride, while the Moonroof allows you to bask in the natural light.

Designed with the driver in mind, the 2 Series boasts a sleek and sophisticated exterior, complemented by a well-appointed interior that exudes refined elegance. The Perforated Sensatec upholstery and Sport Seats provide both style and comfort, while the Power Front Seats and Memory Seat function allow you to find your perfect driving position.

Safety is a top priority in the 2 Series, with features like Adaptive Cruise Control, Automatic High Beams, and a comprehensive suite of airbags and driver-assist technologies to keep you and your passengers secure on the road.

Experience the pinnacle of performance, technology, and luxury with the 2026 BMW 2 Series 230i xDrive. We invite you to visit our showroom and take this exceptional vehicle for a test drive. Prepare to be captivated by its dynamic capabilities and refined sophistication.

*Untitled Courtesy Vehicle.

**Miles are estimated, not actual.

***ONLINE SALE PRICE INCLUDES BMW FINANCIAL SERVICES FINANCE AND LOYALTY CREDITS. MUST FINANCE THROUGH BMW FS AND QUALIFY FOR LOYALTY TO RECIEVE ONLINE PRICE.

BMW FACTORY CERTIFIED WITH UNLIMITED MILE WARRANTY

This 2026 BMW 4 Series 430i xDrive is a true masterpiece of engineering, combining the brand's renowned performance and luxury in a sleek and sophisticated package. Boasting a stunning Dravit Grey Metallic exterior, this vehicle is sure to turn heads wherever it goes.

• M Sport Package
• M Sport Package (337)
• M Sport Package Pro
• Parking Assistance Package
• Premium Package
• Shadowline Package
• harman/kardon Surround Sound System
• Comfort Access Keyless Entry
• Remote Engine Start
• Variable Sport Steering
• Power Tailgate
• Aerodynamic Kit
• Black Mirror Caps
• Extended Shadowline Trim
• Full LED Headlights w/Laserlight Taillights
• M Shadowline Lights
• M Sport Suspension
• Rear Spoiler
• Shadowline Exterior Trim
• Without Lines Designation Outside

Under the hood, this 4 Series is powered by a 2.0L 4-Cylinder TwinPower Turbo engine, delivering an impressive 27 city/34 highway MPG. The 8-Speed Automatic Sport transmission and xDrive all-wheel-drive system ensure exceptional handling and control, no matter the road conditions.

The interior of this 430i xDrive is equally impressive, with a wealth of premium features that elevate the driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of Remote Engine Start, Power Tailgate, and Heated Steering Wheel, while the Live Cockpit Pro with Navigation and Wireless Device Charging keep you connected and entertained. The harman/kardon Surround Sound System provides an immersive audio experience, while the Parking Assistant Plus and Surround View Camera ensure effortless maneuverability.

This BMW Certified Pre-Owned vehicle comes with the peace of mind of a comprehensive Multipoint Inspection, Roadside Assistance, and a Transferable Warranty with a $0 deductible. Experience the ultimate in luxury and performance with this exceptional 2026 BMW 4 Series 430i xDrive.

Embark on a journey of luxury with Motor Werks Perks, where exclusivity awaits at every turn. Unveil a world of unparalleled privileges designed to elevate your experience. Immerse yourself in the rich aroma of our in-store Starbucks, where every sip is a decadent delight. Effortlessly maintain your vehicle's pristine shine with the swift efficiency of Wash Werks express lane car wash. Seamlessly transition through your day with the convenience of our service loaners, ensuring your mobility knows no bounds. Surrender to the pinnacle of service with our valet service pick-up and drop-off, where every detail is meticulously crafted for your satisfaction. For over 50 illustrious years, Motor Werks has been Driven By You, dedicated to surpassing expectations and defining excellence.

description: 2009 Chevrolet Corvette Coupe 3LT Z51 Crystal Red Metallic with 9,700 miles for $36,500 Crystal Red Metallic looks deep and rich in the sun, and this Corvette wears it well. It?s a Southern car since new, clean Carfax, and garage kept, so it shows the kind of care you hope to find but rarely do. With only 9,700 miles, it still feels tight and fresh. Under the hood is the 6.2L LS3 V8 (436 hp) paired with a 6-speed automatic and a 2.73 rear axle ratio. It pulls hard when you ask, then settles down for an easy cruise. The Z51 Performance Package and Dual Mode Performance Exhaust give it that sharp, planted feel, with a sound that wakes up when you lean in. The 5-spoke forged chrome wheels finish the stance just right. Inside, the 3LT trim brings the upscale touch. Cashmere leather, heated power seats, driver memory, and a Heads Up Display keep it comfortable and focused. Dual-zone climate control, Bose audio, navigation, Bluetooth for phone, and XM Radio make it an easy car to live with. You also get keyless entry, universal home remote, cruise control, OnStar, fog lights, and steering-wheel controls. A low-mile, well-kept C6 in a standout color, and ready for the next garage. Introducing the 2025 Tesla Model 3 Performance AWD, a Carfax 1-Owner gem that combines cutting-edge technology with exhilarating performance. Inside, you'll find a sleek and modern cabin with Black vegan leather seat trim, providing a sophisticated and sustainable environment for both driver and passengers. The Model 3 Performance AWD is equipped with zero-emission power from its 0-cylinder electric drivetrain, delivering remarkable acceleration and seamless all-wheel-drive capabilities. This vehicle is packed with advanced safety features, including active cruise control, a blind spot monitor, forward collision warning, and lane departure warning, ensuring peace of mind on every journey. Additionally, the full self-driving capabilities, when supervised, make navigating the roads easier than ever. Comfort and convenience are at the forefront of this Tesla's design, featuring amenities such as heated and ventilated seats, a hands-free liftgate, and rain-sensing wipers. Beneath its sleek White Platinum exterior lies a formidable 5.0L V8 Ti-VCT engine, delivering raw power and precision with every rev. The 6-speed manual transmission offers an authentic driving experience, putting you in complete control of this rear-wheel-drive beast. With a locking/limited slip differential, you ll feel the perfect balance of traction and agility, whether you re cruising down the highway or tackling sharp turns. Safety is paramount, with features like automatic headlights, brake assist, and a comprehensive airbag system, ensuring peace of mind on every journey. The Mustang GT s HID headlights and fog lamps enhance visibility, making night drives as thrilling as they are safe. Inside, the leather steering wheel and smart device integration provide a seamless blend of comfort and technology, while the auto-dimming rearview mirror ensures clarity in any light. For those who crave performance and style, the Mustang GT s aluminum wheels and performance tires promise a ride that s as smooth as it is exhilarating. description:
Discover the perfect blend of power and sophistication with this 2017 Ford Mustang V6. This sleek and dynamic sports car is ready to elevate your driving experience and turn heads wherever you go.

• 6-Speed Automatic (Includes SelectShift, Steering Wheel Paddle Shifters, Remote Start System, Leather-Wrapped Shift Knob)
• 3.7L V6 Ti-VCT 24V Engine
• Rear-Wheel Drive
• 18 City/27 Highway MPG

Boasting a striking black exterior, this Mustang V6 exudes confidence and style. Under the hood, the 3.7L V6 engine delivers an exhilarating 300 horsepower, seamlessly channeled through the smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission with paddle shifters. Whether carving through winding roads or cruising down the highway, this Mustang will provide a thrilling and responsive driving experience.

The interior of this Mustang is equally impressive, with premium features that elevate your comfort and convenience. Enjoy the convenience of the SYNC communications and entertainment system, which seamlessly integrates your smartphone and provides voice-activated control. The leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob add a touch of refinement, while the spacious cabin and split-folding rear seats offer versatility to accommodate your lifestyle.

Safety and technology are also at the forefront of this Mustang V6. Equipped with a suite of advanced safety features, including dual front and side impact airbags, ABS brakes, and electronic stability control, you can drive with confidence knowing you and your passengers are well-protected. The rear-view camera and high-intensity discharge headlights further enhance your visibility and control on the road.

This 2017 Ford Mustang V6 is a true testament to the iconic pony car's blend of performance, style, and sophistication. Whether you're seeking a thrilling daily driver or a weekend sports car, this Mustang is ready to exceed your expectations. Experience the power and passion of this exceptional vehicle by scheduling a test drive today.

description: Discover the versatile 2021 Ford Transit Connect XL Cargo Van, a reliable workhorse designed for businesses and individuals seeking a durable and efficient solution. With a robust 2.0-liter four-cylinder engine producing 162 horsepower, this used van offers impressive fuel economy—24 mpg city and 27 mpg highway—making it an economical choice for daily operations. Its spacious white exterior, complemented by an ebony interior, provides a professional look that’s ready to tackle your cargo needs. Equipped with an 8-speed automatic transmission and front-wheel drive, this vehicle delivers smooth handling and confident performance on the road. With 221,881 miles on the clock, this Transit Connect has proven its durability and readiness to serve your commercial or personal purposes. Designed with practicality and safety in mind, this used Ford Transit Connect features a suite of modern tech and convenience options. A backup camera ensures easy parking and maneuvering, while Bluetooth connectivity allows hands-free communication and audio streaming. Collision warning systems enhance safety by alerting drivers to potential hazards, and the built-in Wi-Fi hotspot keeps you connected on the go. Whether you're managing deliveries or running errands, this cargo van combines functionality with connectivity, making it an ideal choice for those who need dependable performance combined with modern features. 2021 Ford Transit Connect Safety and Security Features This Transit Connect prioritizes safety with essential features such as four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS), which provides optimal stopping power under various road conditions. Emergency braking preparation adds an extra layer of protection by alerting drivers to potential collisions, giving you vital seconds to react. Additionally, the automatic locking feature on the power door locks enhances security when the vehicle is parked or in motion, helping safeguard your cargo and passengers. 2021 Ford Transit Connect Entertainment and Technology Features Stay connected and entertained with the FordPass Connect system, which offers smart device app compatibility for seamless control of vehicle functions from your smartphone. The app includes engine start capabilities, allowing remote ignition for added convenience. description:
Introducing the 2024 Chevrolet Camaro 1LT - a sports car that combines style, performance, and advanced technology to deliver an unparalleled driving experience. With its sleek, aerodynamic design and powerful 3.6L V6 DI engine, this Camaro is ready to take on the open road with confidence.

Key features of this Camaro 1LT include:

- Backup Camera
- Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
- Bluetooth Connectivity
- RS Package with Dark Tint LED Tail Lamps and 20" 5-Split Spoke Machined-Face Aluminum Wheels

The Preferred Equipment Group 1LT further enhances the Camaro's appeal, offering a premium audio system, automatic climate control, and a host of other convenience and safety features.

Slip behind the wheel of this Camaro and you'll be greeted by a spacious, well-appointed interior that puts the driver in complete control. The 8-way power driver's seat and leather-wrapped steering wheel ensure a comfortable and engaging driving experience, while the Bose premium audio system fills the cabin with rich, immersive sound.

But the true heart of the Camaro lies under the hood. The 3.6L V6 DI engine delivers an exhilarating 335 horsepower, channeled through a smooth-shifting 6-speed manual transmission and the rear-wheel-drive system. With a 0-60 mph time of just 5.4 seconds, this Camaro is ready to thrill, whether you're carving through winding roads or merging onto the highway.

Yet, despite its performance pedigree, the Camaro 1LT remains surprisingly efficient, boasting an EPA-estimated 26 mpg on the highway. This perfect balance of power and efficiency makes it an exceptional value proposition in the sports car segment.

Interested in experiencing the 2024 Chevrolet Camaro 1LT for yourself? We invite you to visit our showroom and take this remarkable sports car for a test drive. With its stunning good looks, impressive performance, and wealth of advanced features, the Camaro 1LT is sure to exceed your expectations and leave a lasting impression. Contact us today to schedule your appointment and discover the true joy of driving.

Past Chairman of the Board and CEO John Wiesner was born in Richmond, Texas and grew up in Hempstead. He married Beth Sorsby, also of Hempstead. They were graduates of Southern Methodist University. Mr. Wiesner started his automotive career in Hempstead in 1949, then moved to Baytown. In 1977, he purchased the Buick-Pontiac-GMC dealership in Conroe which is now the main headquarters for the Wiesner Automotive Group. Some cars blend in. This one announces itself before it even turns the key. Finished in unmistakable Rally Yellow over a bold Black interior, this 2012 Chevrolet Camaro Coupe 1LS captures the spirit of modern muscle with a nod to its legendary heritage. With only 46,633 miles, this Camaro is exceptionally well-preserved—low mileage, iconic color, and unmistakable presence. Engineered for the Drive Under the hood sits Chevrolet’s proven 3.6L Direct Injection V6, delivering an impressive 312 horsepower and 278 lb-ft of torque. This isn’t just entry-level muscle—this is serious performance with balance and efficiency. Paired with a responsive 6-speed manual transmission (standard on 1LS), this Camaro keeps you connected to the road in a way automatics simply can’t replicate. Performance Highlights: 3.6L DOHC V6 with Variable Valve Timing 312 horsepower / 278 lb-ft of torque 6-speed manual transmission Rear-wheel drive for true muscle car dynamics Four-wheel independent suspension 4-wheel disc brakes with ABS StabiliTrak® electronic stability control The chassis is rigid, planted, and tuned to deliver confident cornering and strong straight-line acceleration. This Camaro feels solid at highway speeds and aggressive when pushed. 1LS Preferred Equipment Group – Focused & Purposeful The 1LS Preferred Equipment Group delivers the core Camaro experience with essential modern comfort: Power windows, locks, and mirrors Air conditioning Cruise control AM/FM stereo with CD/MP3 capability Steering wheel-mounted controls Keyless entry Everything you need—without unnecessary distractions. This is muscle in its purest form. Rally Yellow with Decklid Spoiler – Iconic Stance The Rally Yellow exterior is more than a color—it’s a statement. It highlights the Camaro’s sculpted body lines, wide stance, and aggressive front fascia. Adding to the performance-inspired look is the decklid spoiler wing, enhancing both aerodynamics and presence. It gives this Camaro that unmistakable performance silhouette that turns heads at every stoplight. Interior – Driver-Focused Muscle Inside, the Black interior keeps the focus where it belongs—on the drive. Deep-set gauges inspired by classic Camaros Supportive sport seats Low-slung driving position Clean, performance-oriented cockpit layout You don’t just sit in this car—you strap into it. Why This Camaro? Extremely low mileage for its year Rear-wheel drive performance 312-horsepower V6 with manual transmission Iconic Rally Yellow exterior Classic American muscle design with modern reliability The 2012 Chevrolet Camaro 1LS represents a time when muscle cars were bold, mechanical, and unapologetic. It’s powerful without being overcomplicated. Exciting without being impractical. This isn’t just transportation. It’s weekend drives with the windows down. It’s the rumble at idle. It’s the feeling of grabbing a gear and taking control.. description: Command the Road with the 2025 Ford Mustang EcoBoost: A Turbocharged Icon in Shadow Black, Designed for Thrill-Seekers and Performance Enthusiasts Alike. Experience the thrill of driving the 2025 Ford Mustang EcoBoost, a masterpiece of engineering designed for those who crave power and precision. Under the sleek Shadow Black exterior, the 2.3L I4 GTDI DOHC Turbocharged engine delivers an exhilarating ride, perfectly complemented by a 10-speed automatic transmission. This Mustang is crafted for drivers who appreciate the seamless blend of performance and style. The rear-wheel-drive system, paired with a locking/limited slip differential, ensures an agile and responsive drive, making every corner a new adventure. Safety is paramount, with features like Blind Spot Monitor, Lane Keeping Assist, and Front Collision Mitigation, providing peace of mind on every journey. The Mustang s intuitive technology, including a back-up camera and smart device integration, keeps you connected and in control. With performance tires and aluminum wheels, this coupe is not just about speed but also about stability and handling. Inside, the Mustang offers a driver-centric experience with bucket seats and a multi-zone climate control system, ensuring comfort on every drive. The 2025 Ford Mustang EcoBoost is more than a car it s an invitation to explore the road with confidence and style.

EMISSIONS, FEDERAL REQUIREMENTS, Engine, 5.7L LS6 V8 SFI, TRANSMISSION, 6-SPEED MANUAL, SEATS, FRONT LEATHER SEATING SURFACES BUCKET, Z06-SPECIFIC, HIGHWEAR NUANCE LEATHER SEAT TRIM, SOLID PAINT, MEMORY PACKAGE,3 DRIVERS, MIRRORS, OUTSIDE REARVIEW, DRIVER & INSIDE ELECTROCHROMIC (LIGHT-SENSITIVE AUTO DIMMING) Base Equipment GroupHead-Up Display Comfort Leather seat upholstery - superior sitting. Theres more class in the cabin with leather seat upholstery. The leather material is luxurious to the touch, offers a distinctive look, and is easy to clean. Put a little luxury behind you with leather seat upholstery. Manual reclining driver seat - Lean back. Gain some space between you and the wheel with manual reclining driver seat. It lets you adjust the angle of the seatback for added comfort while youre driving, or for a more comfortable rest while youre pulled over. Settle in, with manual reclining driver seat. Power driver seat fore/aft adjustment - A touch forward? A touch more back? The choice is yours. Enjoying your drive begins with being comfortable in the drivers seat. With power driver seat fore/aft adjustment, you can find your perfect position to reach the steering wheel and pedals. Not only are you more comfortable, youre safer, too, with power driver seat with fore/aft adjustment.Convenience Cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, cruise control.Safety and Security Head-up display - Keep your head up! You don't have to take your eyes off of the road to get information from your dashboard anymore. With head-up display, important driving information - like speed and RPM's - displays on your windshield in your line of sight. Because when you're driving, the most important information lies on the road ahead. Keep your eyes on the road with head-up display. Come see us at the most unique dealer in the South!!! VIN: WAUTNAF51KA029041 | Stock #: 22414 | Mileage: 78,922
Exterior: Glacier White | Interior: Black | Drivetrain: quattro AWD
Engine: 2.0L TFSI Turbocharged I4 | Transmission: 7-Speed Automatic S tronic
Sleek, athletic, and impeccably engineered, this 2019 Audi A5 Premium Plus quattro Coupe delivers a refined blend of performance, technology, and everyday usability. Finished in Glacier White over a Black interior, the A5s clean coupe profile is accented by Audis signature LED lighting and sculpted body linestimeless design that still turns heads.
Under the hood, the turbocharged 2.0L TFSI engine provides responsive power and impressive efficiency, while Audis legendary quattro all-wheel drive ensures confident traction in all conditions. The quick-shifting 7-speed S tronic dual-clutch transmission delivers seamless acceleration whether youre commuting or carving up back roads.
Inside, the Premium Plus package elevates the experience with premium materials and advanced technology. Audis intuitive layout places controls exactly where you want them, complemented by a driver-focused cockpit and excellent outward visibility. This coupe is as comfortable on long highway drives as it is engaging around town.
Key Features & Highlights


Premium Plus Package


Audi quattro All-Wheel Drive


Virtual Cockpit digital instrument cluster


Panoramic sunroof


Leather seating surfaces with power front seats


Heated front seats


Bang & Olufsen premium audio system


Navigation with real-time traffic


Apple CarPlay & Android Auto


LED headlights and taillights


Dual-zone automatic climate control


Keyless entry with push-button start


Sport suspension for a balanced, confident ride


The A5 Coupe strikes the perfect balance between sport and sophisticationagile handling, refined ride quality, and a cabin that feels truly premium. Its an ideal choice for drivers who want luxury without sacrificing performance or style.
Why Buy From Sports Cars International


Family-owned and operated since 1980


Two convenient Lynnwood locations


Highly rated dealer with thousands of satisfied customers


Hand-selected inventory with thorough inspections


Transparent, no-pressure buying experience


Financing and extended service contract options available

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2019 Dodge Challenger R/T. This powerful muscle car combines bold style, exceptional performance, and an array of premium features that will captivate any driving enthusiast.

Boasting a striking white exterior, this Challenger R/T commands attention on the road. Equipped with an impressive HEMI 5.7L V8 engine and an 8-speed automatic transmission, this rear-wheel-drive coupe delivers an exhilarating driving experience. Enjoy impressive fuel efficiency with an EPA-estimated 16 city/25 highway MPG.

Key features include:
• Blacktop Package
• Cold Weather Group
• Driver Convenience Group
• Blind Spot & Cross Path Detection
• High-Intensity Discharge Headlamps
• 180 Amp Alternator
• Black Fuel Filler Door
• Black Grille with Bezel

• Rear Black Spoiler

• Heated Front Seats

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior, featuring Houndstooth Cloth Performance Seats, Uconnect 4 with a 7" display, and a host of connectivity and convenience features. The driver-centric cockpit and sport-tuned suspension ensure an engaging and responsive driving experience.

Whether you're looking to conquer the daily commute or unleash your inner thrill-seeker on the open road, this 2019 Dodge Challenger R/T is the perfect companion. Experience the power and style that have made the Challenger a legendary American muscle car. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this exceptional vehicle should be your next automotive adventure.

description:
2019 Chevrolet Camaro SS 2SS
VIN: 1G1FH1R74K0130108

This Camaro SS 2SS is pure American muscle with the right look the right power and the right equipment. Finished in Black with a Jet Black interior this car has the aggressive presence buyers want. Black is timeless on a Camaro and it highlights the body lines hood vents and wide stance that define the SS.

Performance :
6.2L V8
455 horsepower
455 lb ft of torque
10 speed automatic transmission
Rear wheel drive

This 6.2L V8 delivers instant throttle response and a deep aggressive sound that makes the Camaro special. The 10 speed automatic keeps the engine in its power band and provides quick smooth shifts whether cruising or accelerating hard.

Exterior :
Black exterior finish
SS performance styling
Functional hood vents
LED lighting
Low wide stance that gives the Camaro its unmistakable look

Black adds value here because it enhances the muscle car identity and never goes out of style. It is the color most buyers picture when they think Camaro SS.

Interior :
2SS premium interior package
Leather seating
Heated and ventilated front seats
Heated steering wheel
Dual zone climate control
Power adjustable front seats
Memory seating

The 2SS package is the key upgrade. It adds comfort technology and premium materials that make this Camaro just as enjoyable to drive daily as it is on the open road.

Technology :
Touchscreen infotainment system
Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
Premium audio system
Heads up display
Push button start
Remote start

Why Buy?
This Camaro SS 2SS offers real V8 power premium interior features and a classic black on black color combination. The 2SS package adds long term value comfort and desirability. This is the Camaro enthusiasts look for because it delivers performance without giving up refinement.

description: Cruise the Streets in Style: Discover the 2019 Chevrolet Camaro 1LT with V6 Power and Advanced Safety Features Step into the world of exhilarating performance and sleek design with the 2019 Chevrolet Camaro 1LT. This Summit White beauty is more than just a car it s a statement. Under the hood, the robust V6 engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission delivers a driving experience that is both dynamic and responsive, perfect for those who crave power and precision. The rear-wheel-drive system enhances handling, making every twist and turn on the road an adventure. Inside, the Camaro 1LT offers a blend of comfort and technology. The leather-wrapped steering wheel and power-adjustable bucket seats ensure a tailored driving experience, while smart device integration and a WiFi hotspot keep you connected on the go. The back-up camera and keyless start add convenience, making your drive as seamless as it is thrilling. Safety is paramount, with features like Brake Assist, Stability Control, and a full suite of airbags, including knee and side airbags, providing peace of mind. The Camaro s aluminum wheels and performance tires complement its aggressive stance, ensuring you not only look good but feel secure on every journey. Introducing the 2019 Honda Civic EX - a refined and dynamic compact car that's ready to elevate your driving experience. This stunning Civic boasts a sleek red exterior, complemented by a host of advanced features that cater to your every need.

Beneath the hood, you'll find a potent 1.5L I-4 DI DOHC Turbocharged engine, mated to a smooth and efficient CVT transmission, delivering an impressive 31 city/40 highway MPG. This powertrain not only provides responsive performance but also exceptional fuel efficiency, making it an ideal choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Key features of this 2019 Honda Civic EX include:

• Radio: 450-Watt AM/FM/HD/SiriusXM Audio System
• Power moonroof
• Forward collision: Collision Mitigation Braking System (CMBS) + FCW mitigation
• Lane departure: Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS) active
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Heated front seats

In addition, this Civic is equipped with a wealth of premium amenities, including:

• 10 Speakers
• Automatic temperature control
• Four wheel independent suspension
• ABS brakes
• Dual front impact airbags
• Dual front side impact airbags
• Electronic Stability Control
• Fully automatic headlights
• Leather Shift Knob
• Reclining Heated Front Bucket Seats
• 17" Alloy Wheels

The 2019 Honda Civic EX is not just a car, it's a statement of refined style and advanced technology. Whether you're commuting to work, embarking on a road trip, or simply enjoying the drive, this Civic will provide you with an unparalleled driving experience.

At our dealership, we pride ourselves on offering exceptional customer service and a wide selection of quality vehicles. We invite you to visit our showroom and experience the 2019 Honda Civic EX for yourself. Let us demonstrate how this remarkable compact car can enhance your daily driving and exceed your expectations.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this Civic your own. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover the true meaning of driving satisfaction.

description: The 2014 Ford Mustang GT is a bold, high-performance muscle car that blends classic American style with modern features. Dressed in a striking Ruby Red Metallic Tinted Clearcoat, this coupe showcases aggressive styling cues, highlighted by HID Xenon headlights and integrated front fog lights that enhance visibility and style. Under the hood, it packs a powerful 5.0L V8 engine, paired with a 3.55 limited-slip rear axle, delivering impressive acceleration and enhanced traction for an engaging driving experience. The Brembo Brake Package adds serious stopping power and complements the GT's performance credentials, making it well-suited for spirited drives or weekend track days. ----Inside, the Mustang GT is just as impressive with Equipment Group 301A, offering upgraded features such as power-adjustable front seats for optimal comfort and control. Keyless entry allows for added convenience, while side impact airbags provide increased safety for passengers. The inclusion of the California Emissions System ensures compliance with stringent environmental regulations, making it a responsible performance choice. A front license plate bracket is installed for regions requiring front plates, rounding out the vehicle's readiness for diverse ownership needs. All told, this 2014 Mustang GT is a striking combination of vintage-inspired design and contemporary performance technology, built for drivers who want classic charm with modern capability.
