description:
Unleash the power of the 2014 Ford Mustang GT Premium, a true icon of American muscle. This stunning black coupe boasts a thrilling 5.0L V8 engine, delivering an exhilarating 435 horsepower and 400 lb-ft of torque, mated to a smooth 6-speed transmission. With its rear-wheel-drive performance and impressive fuel efficiency of 15 city/26 highway MPG, this Mustang GT Premium is the perfect blend of raw power and everyday drivability.

Elevate your driving experience with the impressive list of premium features:

• Voice-Activated Navigation
• HD Radio
• SIRIUS Satellite Radio
• Dual Zone Automatic Temperature Control
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Traction Control
• ABS Brakes
• Low Tire Pressure Warning
• Electronic Stability Control
• Compass
• Illuminated Entry
• Alloy Wheels

Immerse yourself in the Shaker Sound System, delivering a concert-quality audio experience, while the Dual Zone Automatic Temperature Control keeps you and your passengers comfortable. The Electronics Package and Comfort Package further enhance your driving pleasure with features like Heated Front Seats and a 6-Way Power Passenger Seat.

This Mustang GT Premium is more than just a thrilling performance car – it's a true head-turner. The sleek, aggressive styling turns heads wherever you go, with its bold front grille, sculpted body lines, and distinctive rear spoiler. Step inside the well-appointed cabin and you'll be greeted by premium leather-trimmed bucket seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and an array of intuitive controls at your fingertips.

Whether you're carving through winding roads or cruising down the highway, this 2014 Ford Mustang GT Premium delivers an unparalleled driving experience. With just 107,000 miles on the odometer, this well-maintained sports car is ready to take you on the adventure of a lifetime.

Don't let this opportunity slip away. Schedule a test drive today and experience the power, style, and sophistication of the 2014 Ford Mustang GT Premium. We're confident you'll be impressed by its performance, features, and value. Visit our showroom and let us help you make this iconic muscle car your own.

2014 Scion FR-S Monogram

- One Owner
- 68,684 Miles
- Ultramarine Blue Exterior
- Black Interior
- 2" Lift
- 17" Method Wheels Wrapped In 235/55 Hankook Tires
- Original Window Sticker And Owners Manuals

This one-owner 2014 Scion FR-S Monogram is a standout example of Toyota's lightweight, driver-focused sports coupe, finished in the highly desirable Ultramarine Blue. With 68,684 miles, this FR-S has been well cared for and retains the sharp handling and engaging driving experience that made the platform so popular among enthusiasts. Its clean lines, balanced proportions, and low-slung stance give it a timeless, purpose-built look.

The Monogram trim adds premium touches to the black interior, elevating the cabin with upgraded materials and features while still keeping the focus on the driver. The interior remains sporty and functional, offering supportive seating and a simple, intuitive layout that emphasizes connection to the road. Included with the car are the original window sticker and owner's manuals, further highlighting its well-documented, single-owner history.

What truly sets this FR-S apart is its unique setup. A 2-inch lift combined with 17-inch Method wheels wrapped in 235/55 Hankook tires gives the car a distinctive rally-inspired presence while adding extra versatility and road confidence. This setup not only makes the car visually striking but also opens the door for light off-road or all-weather fun, setting it apart from typical FR-S builds.

If you're looking for an FR-S that blends proven sports car dynamics with a unique and adventurous twist, this 2014 Scion FR-S Monogram delivers. With its one-owner background, tasteful modifications, and eye-catching color combination, it's a fun, uncommon take on a modern enthusiast favorite that's ready to be enjoyed.

Comfort

  • Leather seat upholstery - superior sitting. There's more class in the cabin with leather seat upholstery. The leather material is luxurious to the touch, offers a distinctive look, and is easy to clean. Put a little luxury behind you with leather seat upholstery.
Exterior and Appearance
  • First-row power express open/close sunroof - Let more of the outside in. Now you can be in the sun or gaze at the stars from the comfort of your seat, and have a more open cabin during your drive. With one touch of a button, The first-row power express open/close sunroof is a breath of fresh air.
Technology and Telematics
  • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.
  • Wireless connectivity - Strike the cord. Wireless technology makes it easy to place calls without having to fumble with your phone. It integrates your device with the system inside your vehicle for hands-free access. Keep connected and keep your hands on the wheel with wireless connectivity.

description: Introducing the ultimate luxury performance vehicle - the 2015 BMW 650i Coupe. This stunning coupe combines power, style, and advanced technology to deliver a driving experience unlike any other. Under the hood, the 650i boasts a powerful gasoline engine with an 8-speed shiftable automatic transmission. This combination allows for smooth and effortless acceleration, making every drive a thrilling one. The sleek and sporty exterior of the 650i is enhanced by its iconic BMW design elements, including the signature kidney grille and elegant lines. The stylish coupe is also equipped with sport transmission, giving you the option to switch to a more dynamic driving mode for an even more exhilarating ride. Step inside the luxurious cabin and you will be surrounded by premium materials and cutting-edge technology. The 650i boasts a spacious and comfortable interior, making it the perfect vehicle for both daily commutes and long road trips. But the 650i isn't just about looks and performance - it also prioritizes safety. This BMW comes equipped with advanced safety features such as forward collision warning, lane departure warning, and blind spot monitoring, giving you peace of mind on the road. Don't miss your chance to own this 2015 BMW 6 Series 650i Coupe. With its combination of power, luxury, and advanced features, it is sure to impress even the most discerning drivers. Visit our dealership today and experience the thrill of driving a BMW for yourself.

description: The 2015 Dodge Challenger R/T Plus is a bold blend of retro-inspired muscle and modern refinement, offering powerful performance along with a host of premium features. Under the hood lies a potent 5.7-liter HEMI V8 engine that delivers an exhilarating driving experience, while a finely tuned suspension ensures smooth handling and control. The exterior showcases iconic Challenger styling, enhanced by aggressive proportions and distinctive Xenon headlights that offer excellent nighttime visibility. Inside the cabin, drivers are greeted by refined leather seats that provide both comfort and support, reinforcing the car's balance of luxury and performance.----This R/T Plus trim comes equipped with several advanced options designed to enhance convenience, safety, and entertainment. The premium audio system fills the cabin with rich, immersive sound, perfect for enjoying your favorite music on the open road. Modern amenities like automatic climate control keep the interior comfortable regardless of outside conditions, while technologies such as a backup camera and Cross Traffic Alert assist with maneuvering and parking in tight spaces. With its mix of raw power, comfort-focused features, and modern safety technologies, the 2015 Dodge Challenger R/T Plus appeals to drivers seeking a true muscle car experience without compromising on everyday usability.

description:
This one-owner Challenger R/T Shaker rolls in with 86,687 miles and 22 service records that show consistent care. Under the hood, the 5.7L HEMI V8 delivers unapologetic torque through an 8-speed automatic and rear-wheel drive, while the Shaker Package puts the intake front and center rising through the hood like a challenge. Sport suspension and performance steering sharpen the edge, backed by the Super Track Pak for track-ready grip. ParkSense rear assist and a backup camera keep it tight in the city, while the sunroof and rear spoiler dial up the visual punch. Finished in Torred Clearcoat with black interior, this coupe doesnt just echo muscle car heritage it amplifies it. Its built for throttle-heavy mornings, backroad dominance, and parking lot stares. This isnt a weekend toy its a full-time statement. When the engine fires, everything else fades.

description:
Attention driving enthusiasts! Behold the 2015 Dodge Challenger SRT 392, a true performance powerhouse that's ready to ignite your passion for the open road. With its menacing good looks and heart-pounding capabilities, this Challenger is the epitome of American muscle car excellence.

• BLUE TOOTH READY
• KEYLESS ENTRY
• MOONROOF
• SATELITE RADIO
• USB PORTS
• BACKUP CAMERA
• POWER SUNROOF
• RADIO: UCONNECT 8.4 NAV
• RED SEAT BELTS

New Tires Installed

Beneath the sculpted hood of this Challenger SRT 392 lies the legendary SRT HEMI 6.4L V8 engine, mated to a precise Tremec 6-speed manual transmission. This potent powertrain delivers a thrilling 485 horsepower and 475 lb-ft of torque, allowing you to conquer the asphalt with effortless authority. Pair that with the responsive rear-wheel-drive platform, and you've got a driving experience that will leave you grinning from ear to ear.

But this Challenger is more than just raw power. It's also packed with premium amenities that elevate the driving experience. The Uconnect 8.4 NAV system keeps you connected and entertained, with features like GPS navigation, SiriusXM satellite radio, and a high-definition touchscreen display. The adaptive suspension and performance-tuned steering ensure that every corner is tackled with precision and control.

Step inside the cabin, and you'll be enveloped in a world of sporty luxury. The suede and Nappa leather-trimmed performance seats provide exceptional support and comfort, while the heated steering wheel and ventilated front seats keep you cocooned in climate-controlled bliss. The power sunroof invites the outside in, allowing you to bask in the thrill of open-air driving.

This 2015 Dodge Challenger SRT 392 is a true driver's car, blending uncompromising performance with an array of premium features. Whether you're carving through winding roads or cruising the highway, this Challenger will deliver an unforgettable driving experience that's sure to leave a lasting impression.

Discover the ultimate driving experience with this stunning 2015 Dodge Challenger R/T Scat Pack. Boasting a powerful SRT HEMI 6.4L V8 engine paired with a smooth Tremec 6-Speed Manual transmission, this high-performance coupe delivers an exhilarating and responsive ride. Adorned in a bold and eye-catching Green exterior, this Challenger commands attention wherever it goes.

• Leather Interior Group: Includes Heated Steering Wheel, Power Tilt/Telescope Steering Column, Instrument Panel Satin Silver Bezel, Heated Front Seats, Hectic Mesh Interior Accents

This Challenger R/T Scat Pack is packed with premium amenities that elevate your driving experience. The Leather Interior Group adds a touch of luxury, with heated front seats and a heated steering wheel to keep you comfortable in any weather. The Power Sunroof allows you to enjoy the open air and natural light, creating a truly invigorating driving environment.

Slip behind the wheel and you'll be greeted by a host of advanced technology features, including the Uconnect 8.4" touchscreen infotainment system, SiriusXM Satellite Radio, and integrated voice command with Bluetooth. Stay connected and entertained on every journey.

Performance is at the heart of the Challenger R/T Scat Pack, with its potent SRT HEMI V8 engine delivering an exhilarating 485 horsepower and 475 lb-ft of torque. The Tremec 6-speed manual transmission allows you to fully harness this power, providing a thrilling and engaging driving experience. Pair that with the Challenger's iconic muscle car styling, and you have a truly captivating and unforgettable machine.

Whether you're seeking the ultimate daily driver or a weekend warrior, this 2015 Dodge Challenger R/T Scat Pack is the perfect choice. With its exceptional performance, premium features, and striking good looks, it's sure to turn heads and put a smile on your face every time you get behind the wheel. More information about the 2015 Chevrolet Camaro: The Chevrolet Camaro is a modern take on GM's legendary muscle-car, offering strong rear-wheel-drive performance in a low coupe or convertible body style. Some drivers wanting performance approaching that of high-end exotics, will be tempted by the ZL1 which provides outrageous horsepower numbers. description:
Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2015 Ford Mustang EcoBoost Premium. This sleek and powerful sports car boasts an impressive array of features that will captivate the true enthusiast.

Highlights of this exceptional vehicle include:

• EcoBoost Performance Package
• Enhanced Security Package
• Equipment Group 201A
• HD Radio
• Shaker Pro Audio System
• Memory Driver Seat & Mirrors
• HD Front Springs
• Larger Brake Rotors
• Electronic Stability Control
• Active Anti-Theft System
• Larger Radiator
• Blind Spot Info System w/Cross-Traffic Alert

Powered by the potent EcoBoost 2.3L I4 engine, this Mustang delivers an exhilarating driving experience with exceptional fuel efficiency. The 6-speed manual transmission and rear-wheel-drive layout provide the perfect balance of performance and control, allowing you to fully immerse yourself in the driving experience.

The premium interior of this Mustang is both sophisticated and driver-focused. Enjoy the rich sound of the Shaker Pro Audio System, the convenience of the memory driver's seat and mirrors, and the added security of the Enhanced Security Package. The EcoBoost Performance Package further enhances the driving dynamics, with upgrades like a larger rear sway bar, unique chassis tuning, and larger brake rotors.

Whether you're seeking the thrill of an iconic sports car or the practicality of a daily driver, this 2015 Ford Mustang EcoBoost Premium is the perfect blend of performance, technology, and style. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive at our showroom. We're confident that this Mustang will exceed your expectations and leave a lasting impression.

Don't miss the opportunity to own this exceptional sports car. Contact us today to learn more about this remarkable 2015 Ford Mustang EcoBoost Premium.

description: We know you're going to love our 2015 INFINITI Q60 S Limited Coupe that's dressed to impress in Graphite Shadow! Powered by a 3.7 Liter V6 offering 330hp that is perfectly matched to a 6 Speed Manual transmission for fun passing. With the sport-tuned suspension, large brakes, and quick steering, our Rear Wheel Drive Q60 delivers a lively ride, soaring to 60mph in under 6 seconds and scoring nearly 26mpg on the road. Beautiful inside and out, our Q60 Limited turns heads with its flowing lines and muscular physique that is accented by unique gloss black alloy wheels, a black grille, and a black trunk lid spoiler. Open the door to our Q60 Limited and find a sunroof, heated leather seats with driver memory settings, keyless ignition, dual-zone automatic climate control, and an auto-dimming rearview mirror. The technology is a breeze to use with a prominent touchscreen, voice controls, Navigation, Bluetooth,, great Bose sound system with available satellite radio, and an iPod/USB audio interface. Confidence comes standard in our INFINITI with rear parking sensors, ABS, stability/traction control, front side airbags, advanced airbags, and a rearview camera. Every aspect of the Q60 Coupe has been thoughtfully designed for comfort, elegance, and intuitive function. Reward yourself with this multi-talented coupe that is both elegant and sporty. Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2015 Chevrolet Camaro 2LT. Inside, the Camaro's premium audio system with navigation keeps you connected and entertained on the road. With its exceptional handling, impressive power, and host of advanced features, this 2015 Chevrolet Camaro 2LT is the ultimate sports car for the discerning driver. Don't miss your chance to make this Camaro 2LT your own. Schedule a test drive today and discover the joy of driving a true American icon.

description: Get ready to rev your engines and hit the road in this sleek and stylish Gray 2015 Lexus RC 350! This luxury coupe is not just a pretty face - it packs a powerful punch with its 3.5L V6 engine, making every drive an exhilarating experience. The transmission with Driver Selectable Mode ensures a smooth ride whether you're cruising through city streets or blazing down the highway.With full-time all-wheel drive, you'll feel confident and in control no matter what the road conditions may be. The 3.77 Axle Ratio and Electric Power-Assist Speed-Sensing Steering add to the agile and responsive handling of this impressive vehicle. The double wishbone front suspension and multi-link rear suspension provide a stable and comfortable ride, while the 4-wheel disc brakes offer reliable stopping power.Step inside the luxurious cabin and you'll find a host of convenient features designed to enhance your driving experience. The dual zone automatic air conditioning keeps you and your passengers comfortable, while the leatherette door trim and leather/metal-look gear shifter add a touch of elegance. The front seats include power rear seat easy entry, making it a breeze for everyone to hop in and hit the road.Stay connected on the go with Bluetooth wireless phone connectivity and real-time traffic display. The audio theft deterrent system and home link garage door transmitter provide added peace of mind when you're away from your vehicle. The 60-40 folding bench front facing fold forward rear seatback offers plenty of versatility for cargo and passengers alike.Safety is a top priority in this Lexus RC 350, with features like side impact beams, tire specific low tire pressure warning, and dual stage driver and passenger front airbags. The included first aid kit and outboard front lap and shoulder safety belts further enhance peace of mind for you and your passengers.To top it off, a Carfax report is available for this vehicle, giving you added confidence in your purchase. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this fantastic Gray 2015 Lexus RC 350 - it's the perfect combination of style, performance, and luxury all in one stunning package. Do not hesitate to ask to have this vehicle delivered to your home! We have local and nationwide delivery! We have done thousands of out of state deliveries and it is very affordable! Thank you for your interest and the opportunity to work with you. Please call or text Michael at 978-387-3524Visit Route 110 Auto Sales online at www.route110auto.com to see more pictures of this vehicle call or text us at 978-387-3524 today to schedule your test drive. The advertised internet sales price does not include state sales tax, title, registration and dealer service fees.

Introducing the 2015 Lexus RC 350, a stunning and sophisticated sports coupe that combines exceptional performance with unparalleled luxury. This meticulously maintained vehicle is now available at Grieco Ford of Fort Lauderdale, and it's the perfect choice for the discerning driver who demands the best.

• Leather Seats
• Bluetooth
• Backup Camera
• All Routine Maintenance Up To Date
• Local Trade
• Bought and Serviced at Grieco Ford

Under the hood, this RC 350 is powered by a 3.5L V6 DOHC VVT-i 24V engine, mated to a smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission with AWD. With 19 MPG in the city and 26 MPG on the highway, you'll enjoy exceptional fuel efficiency without sacrificing performance.

The Premium Package and Navigation System Package elevate this RC 350 to new heights, offering a wealth of premium features, including:

• Radio: AM/FM/In-Dash CD/DVD & Navigation
• Lexus Enform
• Back-Up Camera
• Blind Spot Monitor w/Rear Cross Traffic Alert

Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a cabin that exudes refinement and attention to detail. Luxurious NuLuxe seating, a tilt and telescoping steering wheel, and a host of advanced technology features make every drive a true pleasure.

Meticulously maintained and with a clean history, this 2015 Lexus RC 350 is a rare find. Backed by Grieco Ford's commitment to excellence, this vehicle is ready to provide you with years of reliable and enjoyable driving. Don't miss your chance to experience the exceptional performance and luxury of this exceptional sports coupe. Schedule your test drive today and discover the difference for yourself.

Victory Auto Store is a family pre-owned car dealership. The store has been operating since 2011. We are located in Stuart, Florida - the Sailfish Capital of the World”.

Victory Auto Group LLC does the business as Victory Auto Store and now has over 100 pre-owned vehicles on the lot. We are proud of the quality used cars we sell and our commitment to meeting our clients' needs. This is apparent in the number of repeat purchases we receive. Whether this is your first purchase with us or one of many, you can count on our devoted sales staff to provide the best possible car buying experience.

Victory Auto Store is your premiere pre-owned automobile dealership. We stock several of the most popular vehicles on the market today. You'll find a large selection of local used cars, trucks, SUVs, vans, and hybrid vehicles. We offer a wide selection of pre-owned Chevrolet, Chrysler, Dodge, Ford, Honda, Jeep, Mitsubishi, Nissan, Pontiac, Acura, Audi, BMW, Lexus, Toyota, Lincoln, Buick, Mercedes, Alfa-Romeo, Huyndai, Kia, Volvo, Porsche, Volkswagen and Subaru cars.

The present service region extends over Central and South Florida, including Miami-Dade, Broward, Treasure Coast, and Palm Beach counties, as well as Martin County, Port St. Lucie, and Vero Beach.

We are pleased to service our community and neighbors in Stuart, Palm City, Jupiter, Port Saint Lucie, Port Salerno, Indiantown, Fort Pierce, Jensen Beach, Hobe Sound, Ft. Lauderdale, Orlando, Tampa, Sarasota, Miami, North Palm Beach, Palm Beach Gardens, Vero Beach, West Palm Beach, and beyond.

description: The 2013 Ford Mustang Boss 302 is a high-performance muscle car that stands out with its aggressive styling, track-ready capabilities, and exhilarating driving experience. Designed for enthusiasts who value raw power and precision handling, the Boss 302 features a specially tuned 5.0-liter V8 engine that produces 444 horsepower. This power is matched with a finely calibrated suspension system and a six-speed manual transmission, giving drivers full control over every shift and turn. The exterior design carries bold lines, unique Boss striping, and a revised front fascia that enhances both style and aerodynamics. Xenon headlights provide improved nighttime visibility while adding a modern touch to the classic Mustang silhouette.----Inside, the 2013 Boss 302 offers a blend of comfort and functionality. Power seats allow for easy adjustments to find the perfect driving position, while Bluetooth connectivity enables hands-free calling and music streaming, ensuring convenience without distraction. The vehicle is satellite radio ready, expanding entertainment options on long drives. Keyless entry adds practicality, making it easier to access the car without fumbling for keys. Safety is also a priority, with side impact airbags contributing to occupant protection in the event of a collision. Altogether, the 2013 Mustang Boss 302 combines the soul of a race car with everyday usability, making it an appealing choice for those seeking both performance and modern amenities.

The CLEAN TITLE, 2013 Dodge Challenger 2dr Cpe R/T in Granite Crystal Metallic is a striking blend of classic American muscle and modern performance. Boasting a formidable 5.7L V8 engine, this vehicle delivers an exhilarating driving experience with the power to match its bold appearance. Its Dark Slate Gray interior is designed to provide both comfort and style, offering drivers a premium environment. Equipped with the Blacktop Package, the Challenger R/T enhances its aggressive demeanor with black exterior accents, while the Mopar Exterior Appearance Group adds further customization with features designed for enthusiasts. The R/T Redline Group amplifies the sporty vibe, integrating red accents and sharp detailing that set this model apart from the rest. Additionally, the Sound Group II ensures your road trips are accompanied by stellar audio quality, immersing you in a rich soundscape. Rolling on 20" x 8.0" aluminum chrome clad wheels, the Challenger R/T not only performs well on the road but also makes a powerful visual statement. The sophisticated Granite Crystal Metallic paint underscores the muscular stance of this vehicle, reflecting its heritage and contemporary appeal. With features tailored for both the thrill seeker and the style aficionado, this Dodge Challenger 2dr Cpe R/T offers an ideal blend of performance, design, and luxury. Whether you're cruising down the highway or dominating the city streets, this Challenger is an embodiment of power, style, and tradition. WE ALSO HAVE NEW DUMP, FLAT AND CARGO TRAILERS ON HAND FOR ALL OF YOUR DUMPING, HAULING AND STORAGE NEEDS. 2013 Dodge Challenger R/T – 5.7L HEMI V8 – RWD – Classic Muscle Coupe If you’re searching for a true V8 muscle car in Woodburn, Salem, Albany, Canby, Vancouver, Eugene, Medford, the Portland metro area, or even Seattle, this 2013 Dodge Challenger R/T is exactly what you want. Powered by the legendary 5.7L HEMI V8, this Challenger delivers strong acceleration, an unmistakable exhaust sound, and classic rear-wheel-drive performance. The R/T trim gives you the perfect balance of muscle-car power and everyday drivability. Key Highlights: ✔ 5.7L HEMI V8 — powerful & proven ✔ Rear-Wheel Drive — true muscle-car feel ✔ R/T performance suspension ✔ Sporty coupe styling that turns heads ✔ Bluetooth & modern convenience features ✔ Comfortable enough for daily driving ✔ Lower cost than newer muscle cars with the same power This Challenger is perfect for enthusiasts, weekend drivers, or anyone who wants real muscle-car performance without paying new-car prices. If you’re shopping locally in Woodburn or coming from Salem, Albany, Canby, Vancouver, Eugene, Medford, the Portland area, or even Seattle, this 2013 Challenger R/T HEMI is absolutely worth the drive. description:
This 2002 Porsche 911 Carrera is a true driver's dream, combining exceptional performance, timeless style, and an array of premium features that will elevate your driving experience. With its sleek gray exterior and powerful 3.6L H6 engine, this Carrera is a testament to Porsche's engineering excellence.

Among the standout features of this vehicle are:

, Navigation System
, Comfort Package
, Heated Front Seats Package
, Leather Tiptronic Shift Gate
, Hi-Fi Sound System
, Bi-Xenon Headlights
, Sport Exhaust System
, Power Moonroof
, Carrera Rear Spoiler
, Leather Steering Wheel

Step inside this 911 Carrera, and you'll be greeted by a cabin that exudes sophistication and attention to detail. The comfortable leather seating, coupled with the intuitive controls and driver-focused cockpit, create an environment that seamlessly blends form and function.

The Carrera's powerful 3.6L H6 engine and rear-wheel-drive configuration deliver an exhilarating driving experience, with a 0-60 mph time of just 4.8 seconds and a top speed of 177 mph. The precise handling and responsive steering will have you carving through corners with confidence and precision.

Fuel efficiency is also a strong point, with an EPA-estimated 18 mpg in the city and 26 mpg on the highway, allowing you to enjoy the open road without frequent stops.

This 2002 Porsche 911 Carrera is a true icon of automotive design and performance, offering a driving experience that is both thrilling and refined. With its exceptional features, impressive power, and timeless style, this Carrera is a must-see for any enthusiast seeking a true sports car experience.

To schedule a test drive and experience the joy of owning this remarkable Porsche, please don't hesitate to contact us.
